中文字符串:
发生器类型：
    None 没有发生器
    XRay X射线发生器
    BetaRay Beta射线发生器
Chinese string: Generator type: None No generator XRay X-ray generator BetaRay Beta ray generator

中文字符串: 设备最大测量长度，即设备的最大可能行程【绝对坐标】（单位：毫米）
Chinese string: The maximum measuring length of the device, that is, the maximum possible travel of the device [absolute coordinates] (unit: mm)

中文字符串: 设备有效测量范围起点位置（在设备有效测量范围内不应该有类似标准片这样的部件）【已改为逻辑坐标】，单位：毫米。
Chinese string: The starting point of the effective measuring range of the device (there should be no components such as standard pieces within the effective measuring range of the device) [has been changed to logical coordinates], unit: millimeter.

中文字符串: 设备有效测量长度（注意与设备最大测量长度进行区分，从设备有效测量范围起点开始算起），该长度表示在这个长度范围内取到的面密度数据是有效的，这个长度范围内不应该有类似标准片这样的部件【已改为逻辑坐标】，单位：毫米。
Chinese string: The effective measurement length of the device (note that it should be distinguished from the maximum measurement length of the device, and is measured from the starting point of the effective measurement range of the device). This length indicates that the surface density data obtained within this length range is valid. There should be no components such as standard sheets within this length range [changed to logical coordinates]. Unit: millimeter.

中文字符串: 限位趟判定标准，当Y最大坐标超过设备最大量程多少毫米时，认为该趟属于限位趟，单位：毫米，默认值10。\r\n      注意：如果设备为同步带的则没有限位趟的概念，因为采用同步带时发生器与探测器总是同步的，这个值可以设置为0，表示不开启限位趟检测。
Chinese string: Limit trip judgment standard, when the maximum Y coordinate exceeds the maximum range of the device by how many millimeters, it is considered to be a limit trip, unit: millimeter, default value 10. \r\n Note: If the device is a synchronous belt, there is no concept of limit trip, because the generator and detector are always synchronized when using a synchronous belt. This value can be set to 0, indicating that limit trip detection is not enabled.

中文字符串: 零点文件分区大小（单位：毫米）
Chinese string: Zero point file partition size (unit: mm)

中文字符串: 动态单零点测零时扩展宽度，单位：毫米
Chinese string: The expansion width when the dynamic single zero point is measured, unit: mm

中文字符串: 单零点与分区零点测量最大允许的间隔时间，单位：分钟
Chinese string: The maximum allowable interval time between single zero point and partition zero point measurement, unit: minute

中文字符串: 当零点采集方式为动态时，单零点是否区分正反向，是：True，否：False
Chinese string: When the zero point acquisition mode is dynamic, whether the single zero point distinguishes between positive and negative directions, yes: True, no: False

中文字符串: 单零点修正EWMA算法权重，浮点数，[0,1]，值为0时相当于关闭算法。
Chinese string: Single zero-point correction EWMA algorithm weight, floating point number, [0,1]. A value of 0 is equivalent to turning off the algorithm.

中文字符串: 分区零点修正各分区位置数据权重占比，浮点数，范围[0,1]，值为1时相当于关闭算法。
Chinese string: Partition zero point correction is the weight ratio of each partition position data, floating point number, range [0,1], when the value is 1, it is equivalent to turning off the algorithm.

中文字符串: 定位到什么位置进行开关Beta源操作（仅对通过软件开关源按钮起作用），单位：毫米，浮点数，当此值小于0时，不需要自动定位到该位置。
Chinese string: The position to be positioned for the Beta source switch operation (only works when the source switch button is turned on and off via software). Unit: mm, floating point number. When this value is less than 0, there is no need to automatically position to this position.

中文字符串: 启动/复位扫描安全距离，即软件保证留足足够长的安全距离让运动控制板正常复位，防止设备启动即卡住的事情发生。\r\n    保护规则：启动/复位扫描时，当前坐标位置大于设备最大行程的一半且该设定值大于0会触发本保护机制，即自动定位到 设备最大行程/2-设定值 位置，然后再启动/复位扫描。\r\n    设定值大于0时生效，单位：毫米，浮点数。
Chinese string: Start/reset scanning safety distance, that is, the software ensures that there is enough safety distance to allow the motion control board to reset normally, to prevent the device from getting stuck when it starts. \r\n Protection rule: When starting/resetting scanning, if the current coordinate position is greater than half of the device's maximum stroke and the set value is greater than 0, this protection mechanism will be triggered, that is, the device will automatically be positioned to the maximum stroke/2-set value position, and then start/reset scanning. \r\n It takes effect when the set value is greater than 0, unit: mm, floating point number.

中文字符串: 扫描架类型：\r\n    C， C型架\r\n    O， O型架
Chinese string: Scanning frame type:\r\n C, C-frame\r\n O, O-frame

中文字符串: 固定扫描区间范围，设定后开始菜单下启动扫描功能将强制设定为该参数指定的区间，格式为“0,1000”，“,”号前后分别为扫描区间的起点和终点，浮点数。
Chinese string: Fixed scanning interval range. After setting, the scanning function started in the start menu will be forced to be set to the interval specified by this parameter. The format is "0,1000". The "," before and after the sign are the starting point and end point of the scanning interval respectively, and it is a floating point number.

中文字符串: 开始菜单下启动扫描功能是否以原点回归模式启动扫描，若为否，则采用区间扫描模式，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to start the scan function in the start menu in the origin return mode. If not, the interval scan mode is used. Yes: True, No: False.

中文字符串:
运动控制板协议版本，目前包含以下版本：
        V1, 适用于20190919之前生产的运动控制板
        V2, 对应运动控制板第二代版本，支持多架功能
        V2Laser, 对应运动控制板第二代激光版本，支持多架功能，支持射线+激光双4K数据传输速率
        V3, 对应运动控制板第三代版本，支持40K激光数据传输速率
        V4, 对应运动控制板第四代版本，支持50K激光+射线数据传输速率
Chinese string:
The motion control board protocol version currently includes the following versions:
 V1, applicable to motion control boards produced before 20190919
 V2, corresponding to the second generation version of the motion control board, supports multi-frame function
 V2Laser, corresponding to the second generation laser version of the motion control board, supports multi-frame function, supports ray + laser dual 4K data transmission rate
 V3, corresponding to the third generation version of the motion control board, supports 40K laser data transmission rate
 V4, corresponding to the fourth generation version of the motion control board, supports 50K laser + ray data transmission rate

中文字符串:
设备支持的扩展设备功能，目前包含以下功能（每项功能以英文“,”号隔开）：
        Tec， 支持TEC功能，即发生器温控装置；
        AdvancedLightSoundControl， 支持高级声光控制功能，高级声光控制功能需要与运动控制板程序对应，不可随意修改；
        Tec2, 支持TEC2功能，即探测器温控装置；

Chinese string: Number of days to retain raw data

中文字符串: 原始数据保存位置（留空使用默认路径“%LocalAppData%\\Pure”，如需自定义路径，则要求该路径必须为绝对路径，如：D:\\RawData，且需确保该文件夹已存在）
Chinese string: Raw data save location (leave it blank to use the default path "%LocalAppData%\\Pure". If you need to customize the path, the path must be an absolute path, such as: D:\\RawData, and make sure the folder exists)

中文字符串: Tgdamc设备是否使用软动态零点测量范围，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether the Tgdamc device uses soft dynamic zero measurement range, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: Tgdamc设备V2协议是否使用移动色标状态代替固定色标状态，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether the Tgdamc device V2 protocol uses the moving color mark state instead of the fixed color mark state, yes: True, no: False.
The amount by which the signal value is offset, an integer.

中文字符串: 设备可能最大抖动距离，当发现一趟长度小于此值时，可认为设备存在抖动，当此值为0时相当于关闭此抖动点检测功能，是：True，否：False
Chinese string: The maximum possible jitter distance of the device. When a trip length is less than this value, it is considered that the device is jittering. When this value is 0, it is equivalent to turning off the jitter point detection function. Yes: True, No: False

中文字符串: 每Trip（趟）最小长度（单位：毫米）
趟判定走带灵敏度（按位移），单位：与X坐标一致，用于判断在一次趟扫描中，涂布方向有没有位移，它是判定本趟数据中是否可能含有头尾极片边界点、单双面交界点的依据
Chinese string: The sensitivity of the tape is determined by displacement. The unit is the same as the X coordinate. It is used to determine whether there is displacement in the coating direction during a scan. It is the basis for determining whether the data of this scan may contain the boundary points of the head and tail pole pieces and the intersection points of the single and double sides.

中文字符串: 秒判定走带灵敏度（按时间），单位：与X坐标一致，用于判断在一秒钟内，涂布方向有没有位移，它是实时判定是否走带的依据，用于 立即打标 等功能进行判定时所使用。
Chinese string: Seconds to determine the tape feed sensitivity (by time), unit: consistent with the X coordinate, used to determine whether there is displacement in the coating direction within one second. It is the basis for real-time determination of whether the tape is feeding, and is used for determination of immediate marking and other functions.

中文字符串: 程序允许的最大涂布方向坐标，单位：毫米，当此值大于0 且 设备涂布方向坐标大于此值时，应用自动向设备发送X坐标重置命令。\r\n      设置此参数的目的在于防止涂布坐标过大时损失太多精度，导致头尾提取精度不够，1.6E+07可以保证毫米级的精度，\r\n      但是用户很可能不会在该位置处就停机，因此再放宽至1E+07（10千米）就可以开始重置X坐标。
Chinese string: The maximum coating direction coordinate allowed by the program, unit: millimeter. When this value is greater than 0 and the device coating direction coordinate is greater than this value, the application automatically sends an X coordinate reset command to the device. \r\n The purpose of setting this parameter is to prevent the coating coordinate from losing too much precision when it is too large, resulting in insufficient head and tail extraction precision. 1.6E+07 can guarantee millimeter-level accuracy, \r\n However, the user is likely not to stop at this position, so it is relaxed to 1E+07 (10 kilometers) to start resetting the X coordinate.

中文字符串: 自动重置X坐标前需要涂布方向静止不动的秒数，默认：5秒，整数。将该值设为小于0的整数可强制涂布时按需重置X坐标。
Chinese string: The number of seconds that the coating direction must be stationary before the X coordinate is automatically reset. Default: 5 seconds, integer. Set this value to an integer less than 0 to force the X coordinate to be reset on demand during coating.

中文字符串: 趟跳跃点间隔距离，单位：毫米，当一趟中相邻的两点的距离超过此设定值时，可以认为该趟中含有跳跃点，此时，该趟将被抛弃。
Chinese string: The interval distance of jump points in a trip, unit: mm. When the distance between two adjacent points in a trip exceeds this set value, it can be considered that the trip contains jump points. At this time, the trip will be abandoned.

中文字符串: 当停止扫描后静止多长时间后形成新趟（防止最后一趟停留在缓存中太长时间），单位：秒，浮点数。
Chinese string: How long does it take to form a new pass after stopping scanning (to prevent the last pass from staying in the cache for too long), unit: seconds, floating point number.

中文字符串: 是否仅需要完整趟的数据，是：True，否：False，默认为True，启用后那些不能覆盖扫描范围的趟将不再被输出。
Chinese string: Whether only the complete pass data is needed, yes: True, no: False, the default is True. After enabling, those passes that cannot cover the scanning range will no longer be output.

中文字符串: 被程序认可的完整趟可以比目标扫描范围少的长度，单位：毫米，该值必须大于等于0，该值越大，同一趟数据越容易被判定为完整趟。
Chinese string: A complete pass recognized by the program can be shorter than the target scanning range. The unit is millimeters. The value must be greater than or equal to 0. The larger the value, the easier it is for the same pass of data to be judged as a complete pass.

中文字符串:
边界检测模式：
    Normal, 正常模式（使用探测器信号值检测，可检测出极片边）
    FixedColorTagger, 固定色标模式（使用单一色标固定在来料侧托辊上进行过滤，并配合信号值检测基材边方式，无法检测出极片边，仅支持单道间歇涂布）
    Valley, 波谷定制模式（使用探测器信号值检测，取极片上凹陷形态的数据，而不是突出形态的数据）
    FixedValuesBySubstrate, 相对于基材的固定值列表（使用配方中用户设定的留白/膜区宽度列表确定边界位置，起始位置相对于基材，仅支持连续涂布）
    AdvancedFixedValuesBySubstrate, 相对于基材的高级固定值列表（使用配方中用户设定的留白/膜区宽度列表初步确定边界位置，并在这些位置的附近使用探测器信号值查找更准确的位置，起始位置相对于基材，仅支持连续涂布）
    MovingColorTagger, 移动色标模式（使用与探测器固定在一起的移动色标来进行寻边，不支持单双面边检测）
    OnlySubstrate, 仅基材模式（使用探测器信号值检测最外侧边【使用基材寻峰参数】，将检测到的边视为基材涂层混合边）
    AutoMode, 自动模式（对于连续涂布和不走带时，认为没有头尾，基于基材宽度、涂层宽度自动判别各个峰值点及对应的特性来确定边界点性质，否则，认为有头尾，如果固定色标存在，走固定色标模式，否则，认为是连续涂布直接全部保留。）
Chinese string: Boundary detection mode: Normal, normal mode (using the detector signal value detection, the edge of the pole piece can be detected) FixedColorTagger, fixed color tag mode (using a single color tag fixed on the incoming side roller for filtering, and detecting the substrate edge with the signal value, the pole piece edge cannot be detected, and only single-pass intermittent coating is supported) Valley, valley customization mode (using the detector signal value detection, taking the data of the concave shape on the pole piece instead of the protruding shape) FixedValuesBySubstrate, a fixed value list relative to the substrate (using the blank/film area width list set by the user in the recipe to determine the boundary position, the starting position is relative to the substrate, and only continuous coating is supported) AdvancedFixedValuesBySubstrate, an advanced fixed value list relative to the substrate (using the blank/film area width list set by the user in the recipe to preliminarily determine the boundary position, and use the detector signal value near these positions to find a more accurate position, the starting position is relative to the substrate, and only continuous coating is supported) MovingColorTagger, moving color tag mode (using the moving color tag fixed to the detector to find the edge, single-sided and double-sided edge detection is not supported) OnlySubstrate, Substrate-only mode (use the detector signal value to detect the outermost edge [use the substrate peak search parameter], and regard the detected edge as a substrate-coating mixed edge) AutoMode, automatic mode (for continuous coating and no tape running, it is considered that there is no head or tail, and each peak point and the corresponding characteristics are automatically determined based on the substrate width and coating width to determine the nature of the boundary point. Otherwise, it is considered to have a head or tail. If a fixed color mark exists, the fixed color mark mode is used. Otherwise, it is considered to be continuous coating and all are retained directly.)

中文字符串: 是否限制边界检测范围，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to limit the boundary detection range, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 边界检测起始位置，单位：毫米。
Chinese string: Boundary detection starting position, unit: mm.

中文字符串: 边界检测终止位置，单位：毫米。
Chinese string: Boundary detection end position, unit: mm.

中文字符串:
基材边寻边模式：
    Normal，正常方案，采用 BorderDetectMode 参数一致的基材寻边方案
    ColorTag，色标方案（使用移动色标寻找基材边）
    EdgeSignal，边缘信号方案（使用基材突变信号寻找基材边）
Chinese string: Substrate edge detection mode: Normal, normal solution, using the substrate edge detection solution with the same BorderDetectMode parameters ColorTag, color tag solution (using moving color tags to find substrate edges) EdgeSignal, edge signal solution (using substrate mutation signals to find substrate edges)

中文字符串: 色标补偿偏移量，该色标会随探测器一起运动，单位：毫米，浮点数。若色标在探测器的近原点侧则该值为负值（突变点Y坐标偏大），否则为正值（突变点Y坐标偏小）。
Chinese string: Color mark compensation offset, the color mark will move with the detector, unit: mm, floating point number. If the color mark is near the origin of the detector, the value is negative (the Y coordinate of the mutation point is too large), otherwise it is positive (the Y coordinate of the mutation point is too small).

中文字符串: 探测器色标最小稳定长度（扫描方向），单位：毫米。当稳定长度大于指定长度时，才认为色标状态发生了变化。
Chinese string: The minimum stable length of the detector color mark (in the scanning direction), unit: mm. When the stable length is greater than the specified length, the color mark state is considered to have changed.

中文字符串: 边缘信号方案补偿长度，单位：毫米，浮点数。
Chinese string: Edge signal scheme compensation length, unit: mm, floating point number.

中文字符串: 基材起始位置位于零点信号的比例，浮点数，0-1。
Chinese string: The ratio of the substrate starting position to the zero point signal, floating point number, 0-1.

中文字符串: 固定色标与扫描线的垂直距离（固定在来料侧），单位：毫米，浮点数。
Chinese string: The vertical distance between the fixed color mark and the scanning line (fixed on the incoming material side), unit: mm, floating point number.

中文字符串: 色标最小稳定长度（即色标状态在涂布方向保持稳定的最小长度），单位：毫米。当稳定长度大于指定长度时，才认为色标状态发生了变化。
Chinese string: The minimum stable length of the color mark (i.e. the minimum length at which the color mark remains stable in the coating direction), unit: mm. When the stable length is greater than the specified length, the color mark state is considered to have changed.

中文字符串: 在高级固定值列表寻边方案下，自动找更准确的位置时的搜索半径大小，单位：毫米，浮点数。
Chinese string: In the advanced fixed value list edge search scheme, the search radius size when automatically finding a more accurate position, unit: mm, floating point number.

中文字符串: 正常管电压，单位：伏特，浮点数，留空不起作用。
Chinese string: Normal tube voltage, unit: volt, floating point number, leaving it blank will have no effect.

中文字符串: 正常管电流，单位：微安，浮点数，留空不起作用。
Chinese string: Normal tube current, unit: microampere, floating point number, leaving it blank will have no effect.

中文字符串: 当前坐标与需要定位到的坐标相差多少毫米以内的时候，认为两者是相同的坐标，单位：毫米，浮点数。
Chinese string: When the current coordinates and the coordinates to be located are within a certain number of millimeters, they are considered to be the same coordinates. Unit: millimeter, floating point number.

中文字符串: 是否允许额外补充的零位跟踪功能（当设备长时间不用时自动先进行测零) ，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to allow the additional zero tracking function (automatically measure zero when the device is not used for a long time), yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 当发生器未就绪时是否允许测零，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to allow zero measurement when the generator is not ready, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 是否允许自动调整寻峰参数，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to allow automatic adjustment of peak search parameters, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 计算基材或涂层寻峰下限时，与目标采样值的寻峰峰顶值之间的比率(可以接受的容忍误差比率)，浮点数，默认值为 0.7。
Chinese string: When calculating the lower limit of the peak search of the substrate or coating, the ratio between the peak search peak value and the target sampling value (acceptable tolerance error ratio) is a floating point number with a default value of 0.7.

中文字符串: 自动校正寻峰参数算法支持探测的最小峰值大小，浮点数。
Chinese string: The automatic correction peak search parameter algorithm supports the minimum peak size to be detected, floating point number.

中文字符串: 留白宽判别阈值（色标突变点位置在寻峰曲线左右峰值附近多少范围内时认为存在留白，从而可提取左右留白宽度），单位：毫米。
Chinese string: The margin width discrimination threshold (the position of the color mark mutation point is within a certain range of the left and right peak values of the peak-seeking curve before it is considered that there is margin, so that the left and right margin widths can be extracted), unit: millimeter.

中文字符串: 是否自动纠正错误的X坐标，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to automatically correct the wrong X coordinate, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 当前、后两涂布(X)方向坐标差异超过多少时，认为X坐标错误，单位：毫米。
Chinese string: When the difference between the coordinates in the (X) direction of the first and last coatings exceeds a certain value, the X coordinate is considered to be wrong. Unit: millimeter.

中文字符串: 是否允许检测脏数据，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to allow dirty data detection, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 分区算法从大分区向小分区分区时，最大允许自动填充数据的长度，单位：毫米。当坐标差大于此值时认为坐标不再连续不再自动补充缺失的的数据，目前该参数仅应用于X方向分区。
Chinese string: When the partitioning algorithm partitions from a large partition to a small partition, the maximum length of the automatically filled data is allowed, in millimeters. When the coordinate difference is greater than this value, the coordinates are considered no longer continuous and the missing data is no longer automatically filled. Currently, this parameter is only applied to the X-direction partition.

中文字符串: X方向分区的原始分辨率，单位：毫米。
Chinese string: The native resolution of the partition in the X direction, in millimeters.

中文字符串: 真实光斑半径，用于提取基材区数据，单位：毫米，浮点数。
Chinese string: The actual spot radius is used to extract the substrate area data. The unit is millimeter, a floating point number.

中文字符串: 用于计算涂布位置的X坐标在趟数据Y方向上的偏移量，使用这个偏移量可以提高获取到的X趟起始坐标的稳定程度，单位：毫米，浮点数。
Chinese string: Used to calculate the offset of the X coordinate of the coating position in the Y direction of the pass data. This offset can improve the stability of the obtained X-pass starting coordinate. Unit: mm, floating point number.

中文字符串: 自定义配方涂布类型后缀符，格式为“X;X;X”，英文分号隔开，分别对应基材、单面、双面配方的后缀符号。可留空或部分留空以使用应用默认值。
Chinese string: Custom formula coating type suffix, the format is "X;X;X", separated by English semicolons, corresponding to the suffix symbols of substrate, single-sided, and double-sided formulas respectively. It can be left blank or partially left blank to use the application default value.

中文字符串: 用户数据文件削薄区分区大小，单位：毫米
Chinese string: User data file thinning area partition size, unit: mm

中文字符串: 削薄区提取左右跳过宽度，单位：毫米，浮点数。
Chinese string: Left and right skip widths for skived area extraction, unit: mm, floating point number.

中文字符串: 削薄区提取头尾跳过宽度，单位：毫米，浮点数。
Chinese string: Skip width of the head and tail of the thinning area extraction, unit: mm, floating point number.

中文字符串: 是否使用连续涂布专用削薄区提取模式（仅静止时有效，内部使用缓存边位置进行提取），是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to use the continuous coating dedicated thinning area extraction mode (only valid when stationary, internally use the cache edge position for extraction), yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 原始数据记录分区大小，单位：毫米
Chinese string: Raw data record partition size, unit: mm

中文字符串: 区域名称，替代报表名称中的 {region} 占位符。
Chinese string: The region name that replaces the {region} placeholder in the report name.

中文字符串: 机台号，替代报表名称中的 {machine} 占位符。
Chinese string: Machine number, replaces the {machine} placeholder in the report name.

中文字符串: 是否允许去除数据报表左右两端的空白数据区（可减小报表文件大小），是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to allow the removal of the blank data areas on the left and right ends of the data report (to reduce the report file size), yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 是否允许去除削薄区数据报表左右两端的空白数据区（可减小报表文件大小），是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to allow the removal of the blank data areas on the left and right ends of the thinning area data report (to reduce the report file size), yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 设置后将用户数据报表固定直接输出至此文件夹，必须保证路径存在，否则无法生效，字符串，例如：D:\\MyFixedData
Chinese string: After setting, the user data report will be fixed and directly output to this folder. The path must exist, otherwise it will not take effect. String, for example: D:\\MyFixedData

中文字符串: 是否合并数据报表的日期、时间列，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to merge the date and time columns of the data report, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 轮廓数据记录文件分区大小，单位：毫米。
Chinese string: The partition size of the profile data record file, unit: mm.

中文字符串: 轮廓图表分区大小，单位：毫米，若未填写则使用激光轮廓数据记录文件分区大小。
Chinese string: The partition size of the contour chart, in millimeters. If not filled in, the partition size of the laser contour data record file will be used.

中文字符串: 轮廓数据参考趟数，正整数。
Chinese string: The number of reference passes for the contour data is a positive integer.

中文字符串:
削薄区评价数据值显示方式：
    Percent, 百分比方式，测量值/膜区均值*100%
    Range, 极差方式，膜区均值-测量值
    Value, 测量值方式，测量值
    Offset, 偏差方式，测量值-膜区均值
Chinese string: Display mode of evaluation data value of thinning area: Percent, percentage mode, measured value/average value of membrane area*100% Range, range mode, average value of membrane area-measured value Value, measured value mode, measured value Offset, deviation mode, measured value-average value of membrane area

中文字符串: 默认是否从基材边缘开始输出报表数据（仅输出基材内的数据，并且认为近原点基材边处坐标为0），是：True，否：False
Chinese string: Whether to output report data from the edge of the substrate by default (only output data within the substrate, and assume that the coordinates of the substrate edge near the origin are 0), yes: True, no: False

中文字符串: 是否输出基材留白数据，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to output the blank data of the substrate, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 是否翻转数据报表中的测量数据的横向排列顺序，是：True，否：False。对于多架设备要求一条产线中的所有机台此参数必须保持一致！
Chinese string: Whether to flip the horizontal arrangement order of the measurement data in the data report, yes: True, no: False. For multiple equipment, this parameter must be consistent for all machines in a production line!

中文字符串: 设备动作默认超时时间（单位：秒）
Chinese string: Default timeout period for device actions (unit: seconds)

中文字符串: 确认扫描已停止的默认超时时间（单位：秒）
Chinese string: Default timeout (in seconds) to confirm that the scan has stopped

中文字符串: 确认扫描已停止时，每多少秒发送一次停止扫描命令，正整数。该改进是防止运动控制板未响应第一次停止扫描命令时的一个保险手段。
Chinese string: When confirming that the scan has stopped, send a stop scan command every few seconds, a positive integer. This improvement is a safety measure to prevent the motion control board from not responding to the first stop scan command.

中文字符串: 在X-ray发生器关闭或打开时发送电压/电流启停的等待时间（单位：秒）
Chinese string: The waiting time (in seconds) for sending voltage/current start and stop when the X-ray generator is turned off or on

中文字符串: 等待X-Ray开启的最大等待时间（单位：秒），会等待电压电流正常后才算做X-Ray已开启。
Chinese string: The maximum waiting time (in seconds) for X-Ray to be turned on. X-Ray will be considered turned on only after the voltage and current are normal.

中文字符串: 设备命令超时时间，单位：毫秒，即超过这个毫秒数运动控制板没有给予回应就认为此次命令发送超时了。
Chinese string: Device command timeout, unit: milliseconds. If the motion control board does not respond after this number of milliseconds, it is considered that the command has timed out.

中文字符串: 设备命令最大重试次数，自然数。
Chinese string: The maximum number of times a device command can be retried, a natural number.

中文字符串: 手动寻边时，在多少秒内未找到边界点则放弃寻边并提示超时，单位：秒，正整数。
Chinese string: When searching for an edge manually, if no boundary point is found within a certain number of seconds, the search is abandoned and a timeout is prompted. The unit is seconds, a positive integer.

中文字符串: 等待连接稳定秒数，超过该计时后认为无法稳定连接到设备，放弃连接并报错，单位：秒，浮点数。
Chinese string: Wait for the connection to stabilize in seconds. After this time, the device is considered unable to connect to the device stably, and the connection is abandoned with an error. Unit: seconds, floating point number.

中文字符串: 连接稳定秒数，当连接处于连接状态指定秒数后，认为该连接稳定了，单位：秒，浮点数。
Chinese string: Connection stability seconds. When the connection is in the connected state for the specified number of seconds, the connection is considered stable. Unit: seconds, floating point number.

中文字符串: 图表控件分区大小（单位：毫米），留空时 代表使用文件分区大小作为图表控件分区大小。
Chinese string: The chart control partition size (unit: mm). If left blank, the file partition size is used as the chart control partition size.

中文字符串: 图表控件削薄区分区大小（单位：毫米），留空时 代表使用削薄区文件分区大小作为削薄区图表控件分区大小。
Chinese string: The size of the thinning area partition of the chart control (unit: mm). If left blank, it means using the thinning area file partition size as the thinning area chart control partition size.

中文字符串: 密度趋势图分区大小（单位：毫米）
Chinese string: Density trend graph partition size (unit: mm)

中文字符串: 图表显示范围（公差的倍数。例如，2代表图表显示范围为公差范围的两倍）
Chinese string: Chart display range (multiple of tolerance. For example, 2 means the chart display range is twice the tolerance range)

中文字符串: 边界轮廓图图表显示范围（公差的倍数。例如，2代表图表显示范围为公差范围的两倍），留空表示与其他图表保持一致，浮点数。
Chinese string: The display range of the boundary contour chart (a multiple of the tolerance. For example, 2 means the chart display range is twice the tolerance range). Leave it blank to keep consistent with other charts. Floating point number.

中文字符串: 边界轮廓图是否以中心线为绘制起点，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether the boundary contour is drawn with the center line as the starting point, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 纵向趋势图/CPK最多显示的趟数，单位：趟，自然数
Chinese string: Vertical trend chart/CPK maximum number of times displayed, unit: times, natural number

中文字符串: 纵向趋势图/CPK默认可视趟数，该值应当小于等于最多显示趟数，单位：趟，自然数
Chinese string: The default number of visible trips in the vertical trend chart/CPK should be less than or equal to the maximum number of trips displayed. Unit: trip, natural number

中文字符串: 纵向趋势图/CPK是否在尾部添加数据而不是头部，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether the vertical trend chart/CPK adds data at the end instead of the head, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 密度趋势图最多显示的趟数
Chinese string: The maximum number of passes that can be displayed in the density trend graph

中文字符串: 面密度小于多少时，软件直接显示为0
Chinese string: When the surface density is less than a certain value, the software will directly display it as 0

中文字符串: 是否允许用户使用图表的缩放功能
Chinese string: Whether to allow users to use the zoom function of the chart

中文字符串: 界面实时面密度、信号值显示速率级别（数字越小显示越快，最小允许设置为1）
Chinese string: Interface real-time surface density, signal value display rate level (the smaller the number, the faster the display, the minimum allowed setting is 1)

中文字符串: 自动启停-启动前等待时间下限值（单位：秒）
Chinese string: Automatic start-stop-lower limit of waiting time before starting (unit: seconds)

中文字符串: 自动启停-停止前等待时间下限值（单位：秒）
Chinese string: Automatic start-stop-lower limit of waiting time before stopping (unit: seconds)

中文字符串: 静态零点测量时要求的最低数据采集时间
Chinese string: Minimum data acquisition time required for static zero point measurement

中文字符串: 动态零点测量时要求的最低数据采集周期数
Chinese string: Minimum number of data acquisition cycles required for dynamic zero point measurement

中文字符串: 寻边功能最大允许放宽宽度（单位：毫米）
Chinese string: Maximum allowable relaxation width of edge finding function (unit: mm)

中文字符串: 是否允许输入任意速度值，而非整百的值，是：True，否：False
Chinese string: Whether to allow input of arbitrary speed values, rather than integer values, yes: True, no: False

中文字符串: 是否去除设备厂商Logo，是：True，否：False
Chinese string: Whether to remove the device manufacturer's logo, yes: True, no: False

中文字符串: 软件中显示的位置坐标是否为真实坐标，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether the position coordinates displayed in the software are real coordinates, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 管电压比率，默认为1，修改此值可让管电压测量值按此比率显示。
Chinese string: Tube voltage ratio, the default is 1, modify this value to display the tube voltage measurement value according to this ratio.

中文字符串: 管电流比率，默认为1，修改此值可让管电流测量值按此比率显示。
Chinese string: Tube current ratio, the default is 1, modify this value to display the tube current measurement value according to this ratio.

中文字符串: 修改工程师模式参数时，是否需要强制要求设备未启动扫描，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: When modifying engineer mode parameters, whether it is necessary to force the device to not start scanning, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 自动启停开启时启动/复位扫描是否给予提示，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to give a prompt when starting/resetting the scan when automatic start/stop is turned on, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 图表统计文字模板，留空使用软件内置模板，支持如下占位符： {mean} - 平均值, {weight} - 总重量, {max} - 最大值, {min} - 最小值, {sd} - 标准差, {cv} - 变异系数, {cv.net} - 净重变异系数, {range} - 全距/极差， 格式化标签： balabala 中的文字 balabala 将加粗显示。 balabala 中的文字 balabala 将斜体显示。 balabala 中的文字 balabala 将出现下划线。 balabala 中的文字 balabala 将出现删除线。
Chinese string: Chart statistics text template, leave it blank to use the software built-in template, supports the following placeholders: {mean} - mean, {weight} - total weight, {max} - maximum, {min} - minimum, {sd} - standard deviation, {cv} - coefficient of variation, {cv.net} - net weight coefficient of variation, {range} - range/extreme difference, Formatting tags: The text balabala in balabala will be bold. The text balabala in balabala will be italic. The text balabala in balabala will be underlined. The text balabala in balabala will be deleted.

中文字符串: 自动生成卷功能开启时，最少允许用户设置单卷最多趟数，整数。
Chinese string: When the automatic roll generation function is turned on, the user is allowed to set the maximum number of passes for a single roll, which should be an integer.

中文字符串: 自动生成卷功能开启时，最多允许用户设置单卷最多趟数，整数。
Chinese string: When the automatic roll generation function is turned on, the user is allowed to set the maximum number of passes for a single roll, which is an integer.

中文字符串: 标定/校验超过多少趟未能采集到数据时认为数据采集超时，整数。
Chinese string: The number of calibration/verification trips that fail to collect data before the data collection is considered to have timed out. The value is an integer.

中文字符串: 标定校验测头复位位置，单位：毫米，浮点数。
Chinese string: Calibrate and verify the probe reset position, unit: mm, floating point number.

中文字符串: 单面校验允许修正的最大B值修正量，浮点数。
Chinese string: The maximum B value correction allowed for single-sided calibration, a floating point number.

中文字符串: 双面校验允许修正的最大B值修正量，浮点数。
Chinese string: The maximum B value correction allowed for double-sided verification, a floating point number.

中文字符串: 柱状图、面积图 是否从中心线位置开始显示，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether the bar chart and area chart are displayed from the center line position, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 当设备故障时，是否允许用户通过界面移动探测器（寸动/定位），是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: When the device fails, whether to allow the user to move the detector (jog/position) through the interface, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 是否一次性导出所有配方，是：True，否：False，仅导出当前选中的配方。
Chinese string: Whether to export all recipes at once, yes: True, no: False, only the currently selected recipe will be exported.

中文字符串: 是否启用公差上下界不相等模式，在这种模式下用户可以为公差的上偏差和下偏差指定不同的值，但在配方中将仅显示当前架的公差信息，不再显示单面、双面两种不同的公差信息。启用：True，不启用：False。
Chinese string: Whether to enable the unequal tolerance upper and lower limits mode. In this mode, the user can specify different values for the upper and lower deviations of the tolerance, but only the tolerance information of the current rack will be displayed in the formula, and the two different tolerance information of single-sided and double-sided will no longer be displayed. Enable: True, Disable: False.

中文字符串: 是否在配方中启用膜区公差功能，启用：True，不启用：False。
Chinese string: Whether to enable the membrane area tolerance function in the formula, enable: True, disable: False.

中文字符串: 实时扫描图重命名名称，为空时使用默认名称，否则使用填入的名称。
Chinese string: Rename the real-time scan image. If it is empty, use the default name, otherwise use the filled name.

中文字符串: 断面扫描图（动态）重命名名称，为空时使用默认名称，否则使用填入的名称。
Chinese string: Rename the cross-sectional scan (dynamically). If it is empty, the default name will be used, otherwise the filled name will be used.

中文字符串: 手动寻边是否显示设置扫描范围确认窗口，是：True，否：False，若为否，则寻边成功后自动设置扫描范围。
Chinese string: Whether to display the scan range setting confirmation window when manually finding the edge, yes: True, no: False. If it is no, the scan range will be automatically set after the edge finding is successful.

中文字符串: 异常信息面板最多显示的异常条数，正整数。
Chinese string: The maximum number of exceptions that can be displayed in the exception information panel, a positive integer.

中文字符串: 是否显示异常消息弹窗，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to display the exception message pop-up window, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 实时扫描图缓存输出点数，自然数。代表换数据点数每缓存多少个后才输出，缓存点数越大越“卡”，但性能损耗越少。
Chinese string: The number of points in the real-time scan image cache output, a natural number. It represents the number of data points that need to be cached before output. The larger the number of cache points, the more "stuck" it is, but the less performance loss it will have.

中文字符串: 实时数据列表是否使用渐变色默认值，将在未来版本中删除，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether the real-time data list uses the gradient color default value, which will be deleted in the future version. Yes: True, No: False.

中文字符串: 是否允许创建临时卷，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to allow the creation of temporary volumes, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 用户界面可允许调整的扫描速度上限值，单位：毫米/秒，浮点数。
Chinese string: The upper limit of the scanning speed that can be adjusted by the user interface, unit: mm/s, floating point number.

中文字符串: 是否允许使用快捷键（Ctrl+Shift+Alt+K）激活隐藏的密码登录方式，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to allow the use of shortcut keys (Ctrl+Shift+Alt+K) to activate the hidden password login method, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 是否允许开启设备校验报告功能，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to allow the device verification report function to be enabled, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 配方管理界面规格宽度中所有宽度加在一起与基材宽度的差值最大误差，单位：毫米，浮点数。
Chinese string: The maximum error between the sum of all widths in the specification width of the recipe management interface and the substrate width, unit: mm, floating point number.

中文字符串: 是否自动设置预警公差，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to automatically set the warning tolerance, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 预警公差自动设置比例，这个比例为公差的比例，建议取值范围：(0,1)。
Chinese string: The warning tolerance automatically sets the ratio, which is the ratio of the tolerance. The recommended value range is: (0,1).

中文字符串: 在仅有射线数据源的情况下是否允许显示转换厚度，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to allow display of converted thickness when there is only ray data source, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 是否允许在校验历史中应用B值修正，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to allow the application of B value correction in the calibration history, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 可在校验历史中追加应用B值的最长时间间隔（从校验完成时刻起到当前时间的间隔），单位：小时，浮点数。
Chinese string: The maximum time interval (from the time the calibration is completed to the current time) during which the B value can be added to the calibration history. Unit: hours, floating point number.

中文字符串: 二次项系数小数点位数，自然数。
Chinese string: The number of decimal places for the coefficient of the quadratic term, a natural number.

中文字符串: K值/比例系数小数点位数，自然数。
Chinese string: The number of decimal places of K value/proportional coefficient, natural number.

中文字符串: B值/平移系数小数点位数，自然数。
Chinese string: The number of decimal places for B value/translation coefficient, a natural number.

中文字符串: 校验测量值小数位数，自然数。
Chinese string: Check the number of decimal places of measured values, which should be a natural number.

中文字符串: 标定吸收值小数位数，自然数。
Chinese string: The number of decimal places for calibrated absorption value, a natural number.

中文字符串: 是否允许软件窗口状态从最小化变到最大化时自动还原一次界面布局，用于解决某些情况下图表未完全显示问题，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to allow the software window to automatically restore the interface layout once when the state changes from minimized to maximized, which is used to solve the problem of incomplete display of charts in some cases. Yes: True, No: False.

中文字符串: 高度趋势图参考趟数，正整数。
Chinese string: The reference number of altitude trend graph is a positive integer.

中文字符串: 选项-数据文件-分区大小支持的小数点位数，自然数。
Chinese string: The number of decimal places supported by option-data file-partition size is a natural number.

中文字符串:
测量物理量，用于定义配方管理中显示的参数名称，支持以下物理量：
    Weight, 重量
    Thickness, 厚度
Chinese string: Measure physical quantities, used to define parameter names displayed in recipe management, supporting the following physical quantities: Weight, Thickness,

中文字符串: 软件显示的测量值的单位，留空则不显示。
Chinese string: The unit of measurement value displayed by the software. If left blank, no display will occur.

中文字符串: 是否使用隔离膜模式，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to use the isolation membrane mode, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 是否显示图表方向提示文字，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to display the chart direction prompt text, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串:
图表方向左侧提示文字，格式：提示文字[;边框颜色]。 提示文字支持html标签自定义文字样式，支持以下语法： balabala 中的文字 balabala 将加粗显示。 balabala 中的文字 balabala 将斜体显示。 balabala 中的文字 balabala 将出现下划线。 balabala 中的文字 balabala 将出现删除线。
代表一个换行符 balabala 中的文字 balabala 将变为指定颜色 balabala 中的文字 balabala 背景色将变为指定颜色 边框颜色特别说明，设置为transparent将不显示边框。
Chinese string:
Hint text on the left side of the chart direction, format: Hint text [; border color]. Hint text supports HTML tag custom text style, and supports the following syntax: The text balabala in balabala will be displayed in bold. The text balabala in balabala will be displayed in italics. The text balabala in balabala will be underlined. The text balabala in balabala will be struck through.
represents a line break The text balabala in balabala will change to the specified color The background color of the text balabala in balabala will change to the specified color Border color Special note: If set to transparent, the border will not be displayed.

中文字符串: 图表方向右侧提示文字，参数格式同左侧提示文字。
Chinese string: The prompt text on the right side of the chart direction, the parameter format is the same as the prompt text on the left side.

中文字符串: 图表方向提示文字边距（距图表最两边的距离），单位：像素，自然数。
Chinese string: Margin of chart direction hint text (distance from the two sides of the chart), unit: pixel, natural number.

中文字符串: 默认是否从基材边缘开始输出图表数据（仅输出基材内的数据，并且认为近原点基材边处坐标为0），是：True，否：False
Chinese string: Whether to output chart data from the edge of the substrate by default (only output data within the substrate, and assume that the coordinates of the substrate edge near the origin are 0), yes: True, no: False

中文字符串: 警报与设备异常相关参数
Chinese string: Alarm and equipment abnormality related parameters

中文字符串:
设置不需要声音警报的异常类型，默认内部急停不需要声音警报，建议仅在配置编辑器中修改此选项。部分支持禁用声音的警报类型如下：
        ShellError.SurfaceDensityOverLimit 超限警报,
        ShellError.ZeroError 零位异常,
        ShellError.OilTemperature 油温异常,
        ShellError.DoorOpen 门禁异常,
        ShellError.OutsideGeneratorOff 外部关闭发生器,
        ShellError.VoltageCurrent 电压电流异常,
        ShellError.FindBorder 寻边异常,
        ShellError.OutsideEmergencyStop 外部急停,
        ShellError.NeedFillOil 设备润滑欠佳,
        ShellError.CoolingWaterInterrupt 冷却水中断,
        ShellError.EmergencyStop 内部急停,
        ShellError.InsideGeneratorOff 内部关闭发生器,
        ShellError.OutsidePowerInterrupt 外部电源中断,
        ShellError.ThreeTemperaturesError 温度探测器异常,
        ShellError.OilTemperatureHigh 油温过高,
        ShellError.DataUploadError 数据上传失败,
        ShellError.MotorSyncOverLimit 同步超差,
        ShellError.FormulaOutdated 配方已过期,
        ShellError.DriveFreeSpaceLow 分区剩余空间低,
        ShellError.SpotCheckError 点检异常,
Chinese string:
Set the exception type that does not require an audible alarm. By default, internal emergency stops do not require an audible alarm. It is recommended to modify this option only in the configuration editor. Some of the alarm types that support disabling sound are as follows:
 ShellError.SurfaceDensityOverLimit Overlimit alarm,
 ShellError.ZeroError Zero position abnormality,
 ShellError.OilTemperature Oil temperature abnormality,
 ShellError.DoorOpen Door control abnormality,
 ShellError.OutsideGeneratorOff External generator shutdown,
 ShellError.VoltageCurrent Voltage and current abnormality,
 ShellError.FindBorder Edge finding abnormality,
 ShellError.OutsideEmergencyStop External emergency stop,
 ShellError.NeedFillOil Equipment lubrication is poor,
 ShellError.CoolingWaterInterrupt Cooling water interruption,
 ShellError.EmergencyStop Internal emergency stop,
 ShellError.InsideGeneratorOff Internal generator shutdown,
 ShellError.OutsidePowerInterrupt External power interruption,
 ShellError.ThreeTemperaturesError Temperature detector abnormality,
 ShellError.OilTemperatureHigh Oil temperature is too high,
 ShellError.DataUploadError Data upload failed,
 ShellError.MotorSyncOverLimit Synchronization is out of tolerance,
 ShellError.FormulaOutdated Formula has expired,
 ShellError.DriveFreeSpaceLow Partition free space is low,
 ShellError.SpotCheckError Spot check abnormality,

中文字符串: 警报与设备异常相关参数
Chinese string: Alarm and equipment abnormality related parameters

中文字符串: 同步超差警报超差阈值，即发生器的位置与探测器的位置的相对距离超过设定阈值（单位：毫米）。
Chinese string: Synchronous tolerance alarm tolerance threshold, that is, the relative distance between the generator position and the detector position exceeds the set threshold (unit: mm).

中文字符串: 警报与设备异常相关参数
Chinese string: Alarm and equipment abnormality related parameters

中文字符串: 零点异常警报零点变化率阈值（浮点数，默认值为千分之二）
Chinese string: Zero point abnormal alarm zero point change rate threshold (floating point number, default value is 0.2%)

中文字符串: 警报与设备异常相关参数
Chinese string: Alarm and equipment abnormality related parameters

中文字符串: 配方零点变化率阈值（浮点数，默认值为千分之七）
Chinese string: Recipe zero change rate threshold (floating point number, default value is 0.7%)

中文字符串: 警报与设备异常相关参数
Chinese string: Alarm and equipment abnormality related parameters

中文字符串: 是否启用油温监控功能，是：True，否：False
Chinese string: Whether to enable the oil temperature monitoring function, yes: True, no: False

中文字符串: 警报与设备异常相关参数
Chinese string: Alarm and equipment abnormality related parameters

中文字符串: 油温异常值参考点数（保留多少个点作为正常值参照点）
Chinese string: Number of reference points for abnormal oil temperature values (how many points are retained as reference points for normal values)

中文字符串: 警报与设备异常相关参数
Chinese string: Alarm and equipment abnormality related parameters

中文字符串: 油温异常值错误差（当当前油温与参考点油温平均值差多少算作异常值，单位：摄氏度）
Chinese string: Oil temperature abnormal value error (the difference between the current oil temperature and the average oil temperature of the reference point is considered an abnormal value, unit: Celsius)

中文字符串: 警报与设备异常相关参数
Chinese string: Alarm and equipment abnormality related parameters

中文字符串: 最高油温，超过后关闭X-ray发生器（单位：摄氏度）
Chinese string: Maximum oil temperature, exceeding which the X-ray generator will be turned off (unit: degrees Celsius)

中文字符串: 警报与设备异常相关参数
Chinese string: Alarm and equipment abnormality related parameters

中文字符串: 恢复油温，低于后自动开启X-ray发生器（单位：摄氏度）
Chinese string: Restore oil temperature, and automatically turn on the X-ray generator when it is lower than (unit: Celsius)

中文字符串: 警报与设备异常相关参数
Chinese string: Alarm and equipment abnormality related parameters

中文字符串: 是否启用高油温警报，是：True，否：False。（注意：该选项在油温监控功能开启后才会生效。）
Chinese string: Whether to enable the high oil temperature alarm, yes: True, no: False. (Note: This option will only take effect after the oil temperature monitoring function is turned on.)

中文字符串: 警报与设备异常相关参数
Chinese string: Alarm and equipment abnormality related parameters

中文字符串: 高油温预警值，单位：摄氏度。当采样结果连续多次油温高于此值时，认为是高油温。
Chinese string: High oil temperature warning value, unit: Celsius. When the oil temperature in the sampling results is higher than this value for multiple consecutive times, it is considered to be high oil temperature.

中文字符串: 警报与设备异常相关参数
Chinese string: Alarm and equipment abnormality related parameters

中文字符串: 是否启用电压电流监控（总开关），是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to enable voltage and current monitoring (main switch), yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 警报与设备异常相关参数
Chinese string: Alarm and equipment abnormality related parameters

中文字符串: 电压变化比率（当前电压与设定值的差 / 设定值 最大可以接受的值），默认值，0.0002，表示当前电压与设定值的差别不能超过万分之二。
Chinese string: Voltage change ratio (difference between current voltage and set value/maximum acceptable value of set value), default value, 0.0002, means the difference between current voltage and set value cannot exceed 0.02%.

中文字符串: 警报与设备异常相关参数
Chinese string: Alarm and equipment abnormality related parameters

中文字符串: 电流变化比率（当前电流与设定值的差 / 设定值 最大可以接受的值），默认值，0.0005，表示当前电流与设定值的差别不能超过万分之五。
Chinese string: Current change ratio (difference between current current and set value/maximum acceptable value of set value), default value, 0.0005, means the difference between current current and set value cannot exceed 0.05%.

中文字符串: 警报与设备异常相关参数
Chinese string: Alarm and equipment abnormality related parameters

中文字符串: 是否开启电压电流警报（仅控制警报），是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to enable voltage and current alarm (only control alarm), yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 警报与设备异常相关参数
Chinese string: Alarm and equipment abnormality related parameters

中文字符串: 连续多少秒电压电流都监控到异常才进行警报，单位：秒，正整数。
Chinese string: The number of seconds that the voltage and current must be abnormal before an alarm is triggered (in seconds, a positive integer).

中文字符串: 警报与设备异常相关参数
Chinese string: Alarm and equipment abnormality related parameters

中文字符串: 是否监控外部急停按钮状态，是：True，否：False
Chinese string: Whether to monitor the external emergency stop button status, yes: True, no: False

中文字符串: 警报与设备异常相关参数
Chinese string: Alarm and equipment abnormality related parameters

中文字符串: 润滑警报模式。支持以下模式：\r\n      Mode0, 旧警报模式:仅对导轨运行周期进行提示\r\n      Mode1, 新警报模式：更为全面支持对同步带、点检导轨、轴承座、滑块导轨进行润滑警报
Chinese string: Lubrication alarm mode. Supports the following modes:\r\n Mode0, old alarm mode: only prompts the guide rail operation cycle\r\n Mode1, new alarm mode: more comprehensive support for lubrication alarms for synchronous belts, inspection guide rails, bearing seats, and slider guide rails

中文字符串: 警报与设备异常相关参数
Chinese string: Alarm and equipment abnormality related parameters

中文字符串: 设备机械机构/导轨滑块运行多少万周期后提示用户需润滑，默认值：20， 此值大于0有效
Chinese string: After the equipment mechanical mechanism/guide rail slider runs for a certain number of cycles, the user is prompted to lubricate. The default value is 20. This value is valid if it is greater than 0.

中文字符串: 警报与设备异常相关参数
Chinese string: Alarm and equipment abnormality related parameters

中文字符串: 导轨滑块润滑周期，单位：天，浮点数，大于0。
Chinese string: Guide rail slider lubrication cycle, unit: day, floating point number, greater than 0.

中文字符串: 警报与设备异常相关参数
Chinese string: Alarm and equipment abnormality related parameters

中文字符串: 同步带、点检导轨、轴承座润滑周期，单位：天，浮点数，大于0。
Chinese string: Lubrication cycle of synchronous belt, inspection guide rail and bearing seat, unit: day, floating point number, greater than 0.

中文字符串: 警报与设备异常相关参数
Chinese string: Alarm and equipment abnormality related parameters

中文字符串: 是否启用冷却水中断异常，当发生器是XRay时起作用，是：True，否：False，默认不启用
Chinese string: Whether to enable cooling water interruption exception, which works when the generator is XRay, yes: True, no: False, not enabled by default

中文字符串: 警报与设备异常相关参数
Chinese string: Alarm and equipment abnormality related parameters

中文字符串: 是否检测X-ray在外部被手动关闭，是：True，否：False，默认不启动
Chinese string: Whether to detect whether X-ray is manually turned off externally, yes: True, no: False, not started by default

中文字符串: 警报与设备异常相关参数
Chinese string: Alarm and equipment abnormality related parameters

中文字符串: 灯光与声音是否连接在一起，是：True，否：False，该参数用于兼容三色灯与翁鸣器连接在一起的情况，默认为：False
Chinese string: Whether the light and sound are connected together, yes: True, no: False. This parameter is used to be compatible with the situation where the three-color light and the buzzer are connected together. The default value is: False

中文字符串: 警报与设备异常相关参数
Chinese string: Alarm and equipment abnormality related parameters

中文字符串: 是否监控外部电源中断异常状态，是：True，否：False
Chinese string: Whether to monitor the abnormal state of external power interruption, yes: True, no: False

中文字符串: 警报与设备异常相关参数
Chinese string: Alarm and equipment abnormality related parameters

中文字符串: 外部电源中断后多少分钟后自动关机，单位：分钟，浮点数。当该值为负数时代表禁用此功能，若要开启，建议将此值设定为一分钟及以上。
Chinese string: The number of minutes after which the device will automatically shut down after an external power failure. Unit: minutes, floating point number. If the value is negative, it means that this function is disabled. If you want to enable it, it is recommended to set this value to one minute or more.

中文字符串: 警报与设备异常相关参数
Chinese string: Alarm and equipment abnormality related parameters

中文字符串: 是否监控三温温度异常（该参数仅在存在三温传感器时起作用），是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to monitor the three-temperature abnormality (this parameter is only effective when there is a three-temperature sensor), yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 警报与设备异常相关参数
Chinese string: Alarm and equipment abnormality related parameters

中文字符串: 当三温温度连续多少秒异常（低于最低有效温度ValidLowTemperature）时进行停机警报，单位：秒
Chinese string: When the three-temperature is abnormal for a certain number of seconds (lower than the lowest valid temperature ValidLowTemperature), a shutdown alarm is issued. Unit: seconds

中文字符串: 警报与设备异常相关参数
Chinese string: Alarm and equipment abnormality related parameters

中文字符串:
门禁警报功能启动时，关闭X-Ray发生器的动作模式，所有支持的动作模式如下：
        None 不执行任何操作，选择此项建议开启运动控制板的门禁功能,
        StopMovement 仅停止扫描，选择此项建议关闭运动控制板的门禁功能,
        CloseXRayAndStopMovement 关闭X关机并停止扫描，选择此项建议关闭运动控制板的门禁功能,
Chinese string:
When the access control alarm function is activated, turn off the action mode of the X-Ray generator. All supported action modes are as follows:
 None does not perform any operation. Selecting this option recommends turning on the access control function of the motion control board.
 StopMovement only stops scanning. Selecting this option recommends turning off the access control function of the motion control board.
 CloseXRayAndStopMovement turns off X and stops scanning. Selecting this option recommends turning off the access control function of the motion control board.

中文字符串: 警报与设备异常相关参数
Chinese string: Alarm and equipment abnormality related parameters

中文字符串: 门禁打开时是否启用X-Ray特殊模式，在特殊模式下电压、电流被显示为0，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to enable the X-Ray special mode when the door is opened. In the special mode, the voltage and current are displayed as 0. Yes: True, No: False.

中文字符串: 警报与设备异常相关参数
Chinese string: Alarm and equipment abnormality related parameters

中文字符串: 门禁打开状态监控秒数，当门禁打开多少秒时认为门禁打开，防止误报，单位：秒，整数值，最小允许为1。
Chinese string: The number of seconds to monitor the door opening status. When the door is open for a certain number of seconds, it is considered to be open to prevent false alarms. Unit: seconds, integer value, the minimum allowed value is 1.

中文字符串: 警报与设备异常相关参数
Chinese string: Alarm and equipment abnormality related parameters

中文字符串: 点检异常警报标准片重量变化率阈值（浮点数，默认值为千分之七）
Chinese string: Inspection abnormal alarm standard piece weight change rate threshold (floating point number, default value is 0.7%)

中文字符串: 警报与设备异常相关参数
Chinese string: Alarm and equipment abnormality related parameters

中文字符串: 点检异常缓存个数，当缓存个数为1时，发现异常立刻报告，否则缓存N个且全部为异常时才进行报告，正整数。注意，该参数也适用于点检预警功能。
Chinese string: The number of inspection abnormality buffers. When the number of buffers is 1, an abnormality is reported immediately. Otherwise, a report is made only when N buffers are cached and all are abnormal. It is a positive integer. Note that this parameter also applies to the inspection warning function.

中文字符串: 警报与设备异常相关参数
Chinese string: Alarm and equipment abnormality related parameters

中文字符串: 是否允许点检预警功能，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to allow the spot inspection warning function, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 警报与设备异常相关参数
Chinese string: Alarm and equipment abnormality related parameters

中文字符串: 点检预警标准片重量变化率阈值（浮点数，默认值为千分之五）
Chinese string: Inspection warning standard piece weight change rate threshold (floating point number, default value is 0.5%)

中文字符串: 警报与设备异常相关参数
Chinese string: Alarm and equipment abnormality related parameters

中文字符串: 是否监控风扇停转异常（仅监控运动控制板上传的风扇状态），是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to monitor fan stop abnormality (only monitor the fan status uploaded by the motion control board), yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 警报与设备异常相关参数
Chinese string: Alarm and equipment abnormality related parameters

中文字符串: 是否检测位置反馈错误，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to detect position feedback errors, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 警报与设备异常相关参数
Chinese string: Alarm and equipment abnormality related parameters

中文字符串: 位置反馈错误判定标准（速度倍率），浮点数。判定速度与状态包上传速率一致，实际Y坐标与显示Y坐标相差绝对值超过扫描速度的 设置值 倍率时判定为位置反馈错误。
Chinese string: Position feedback error judgment standard (speed ratio), floating point number. The judgment speed is consistent with the status packet upload rate. When the absolute value of the difference between the actual Y coordinate and the displayed Y coordinate exceeds the setting value ratio of the scanning speed, it is judged as a position feedback error.

中文字符串: 警报与设备异常相关参数
Chinese string: Alarm and equipment abnormality related parameters

中文字符串: 位置反馈错误容错次数，正整数。当位置反馈错误连续发生 设定值 及以上时生成位置反馈错误设备故障异常。
Chinese string: Position feedback error tolerance times, a positive integer. When position feedback errors occur continuously for a set value or more, a position feedback error device fault exception is generated.

中文字符串: 警报与设备异常相关参数
Chinese string: Alarm and equipment abnormality related parameters

中文字符串: 在校验用户输入的基材宽度、涂层宽度时，允许实际扫描结果与理论输入值之间存在的最大差异，单位：毫米，浮点数。
Chinese string: When verifying the substrate width and coating width input by the user, the maximum difference allowed between the actual scanning result and the theoretical input value, unit: mm, floating point number.

中文字符串: 警报与设备异常相关参数
Chinese string: Alarm and equipment abnormality related parameters

中文字符串: 是否开启寻边警报（校验边界点缓存与配方中边界宽度数量是否一致），是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to enable the edge search alarm (to check whether the boundary point cache is consistent with the boundary width in the recipe), yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 警报与设备异常相关参数
Chinese string: Alarm and equipment abnormality related parameters

中文字符串: 是否检测伺服接触器已吸合状态，并在必要时给出提示，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to detect whether the servo contactor is closed and give a prompt when necessary, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 警报与设备异常相关参数
Chinese string: Alarm and equipment abnormality related parameters

中文字符串: 是否允许检测伺服未吸合警报，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to allow detection of servo non-engagement alarm, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 警报与设备异常相关参数
Chinese string: Alarm and equipment abnormality related parameters

中文字符串: 是否检测伺服异常，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to detect servo abnormality, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 警报与设备异常相关参数
Chinese string: Alarm and equipment abnormality related parameters

中文字符串:
伺服通讯参数，伺服支持通过串口或者网口进行通讯。
    串口参数格式：站号, Serial, Com端口名称, 波特率, 奇偶性（None/Odd/Even）, 数据位, 停止位(0/1/2/1.5)，例如：1, Serial, Com1, 9600, Even, 8, 1
    网口参数格式：站号, Tcp, IP地址:端口号，例如：2, Tcp, 192.168.0.7:8081
Chinese string: Servo communication parameters, the servo supports communication through the serial port or network port. Serial port parameter format: station number, Serial, Com port name, baud rate, parity (None/Odd/Even), data bit, stop bit (0/1/2/1.5), for example: 1, Serial, Com1, 9600, Even, 8, 1 Network port parameter format: station number, Tcp, IP address: port number, for example: 2, Tcp, 192.168.0.7:8081

中文字符串: 警报与设备异常相关参数
Chinese string: Alarm and equipment abnormality related parameters

中文字符串: 是否启用打标器异常监控，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to enable marker exception monitoring, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 警报与设备异常相关参数
Chinese string: Alarm and equipment abnormality related parameters

中文字符串: 打标器异常窗口，即打标针连续多少秒没有缩回去时，产生打标器异常，单位：秒，正整数。
Chinese string: Marker abnormal window, that is, when the marking needle does not retract for a certain number of seconds, a marker abnormality occurs, unit: seconds, positive integer.

中文字符串: 警报与设备异常相关参数
Chinese string: Alarm and equipment abnormality related parameters

中文字符串: 是否开启声光警报动画效果（目前仅支持亮灭动画），是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to enable the sound and light alarm animation effect (currently only supports on and off animation), yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 警报与设备异常相关参数
Chinese string: Alarm and equipment abnormality related parameters

中文字符串: 声光警报切换时间间隔，单位：秒，浮点数。
Chinese string: The time interval between sound and light alarm switching, unit: seconds, floating point number.

中文字符串: 警报与设备异常相关参数
Chinese string: Alarm and equipment abnormality related parameters

中文字符串: 是否启用设备初始化失败异常，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to enable device initialization failure exception, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 警报与设备异常相关参数
Chinese string: Alarm and equipment abnormality related parameters

中文字符串: 是否监测电离室信号异常，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to monitor ionization chamber signal abnormality, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 警报与设备异常相关参数
Chinese string: Alarm and equipment abnormality related parameters

中文字符串: 电离室信号有几次不变时认为电离室信号异常，单位：次，正整数，要求此值大于等于3。
Chinese string: The ionization chamber signal is considered abnormal when it remains unchanged for several times. The unit is times, a positive integer. This value must be greater than or equal to 3.

中文字符串: 警报与设备异常相关参数
Chinese string: Alarm and equipment abnormality related parameters

中文字符串: 在真实存在Tec设备时，被控Tec实际温度与Tec调节温度相比，差值超出Tec控制误差多少次时，认为存在Tec调控异常问题。单位：次，正整数。
Chinese string: When there is a real Tec device, when the difference between the actual temperature of the controlled Tec and the Tec adjusted temperature exceeds the Tec control error by a certain number of times, it is considered that there is a Tec control abnormality problem. Unit: times, positive integer.

中文字符串: 警报与设备异常相关参数
Chinese string: Alarm and equipment abnormality related parameters

中文字符串: Tec控制误差，当被控Tec实际温度与Tec调节温度相比，差值超出此值时，可认为存在Tec调控异常。单位：摄氏度，浮点数。
Chinese string: Tec control error. When the difference between the actual temperature of the controlled Tec and the Tec adjustment temperature exceeds this value, it can be considered that there is a Tec control abnormality. Unit: Celsius, floating point number.

中文字符串: 警报与设备异常相关参数
Chinese string: Alarm and equipment abnormality related parameters

中文字符串: IO板监控连续多少秒有警报时，判定为真实警报，单位：秒，正整数。
Chinese string: The number of consecutive seconds that the IO board monitors an alarm is considered a real alarm. The unit is seconds, a positive integer.

中文字符串: 警报与设备异常相关参数
Chinese string: Alarm and equipment abnormality related parameters

中文字符串: 是否启用门禁预警功能（该功能需要IO板支持），是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to enable the access control warning function (this function requires IO board support), yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 警报与设备异常相关参数
Chinese string: Alarm and equipment abnormality related parameters

中文字符串: 是否启用风扇停转警报（该功能需要IO板支持），是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to enable the fan stop alarm (this function requires IO board support), yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 警报与设备异常相关参数
Chinese string: Alarm and equipment abnormality related parameters

中文字符串: 是否监控主站失联异常，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to monitor the master station loss of connection abnormality, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 警报与设备异常相关参数
Chinese string: Alarm and equipment abnormality related parameters

中文字符串: 是否开启数据采集预警，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to enable data collection warning, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 警报与设备异常相关参数
Chinese string: Alarm and equipment abnormality related parameters

中文字符串: 数据采集预警监控趟数，当连续N趟未采集到目标数据时，触发数据采集预警警报，单位：趟，正整数。
Chinese string: The number of data collection warning monitoring passes. When the target data is not collected for N consecutive passes, the data collection warning alarm is triggered. The unit is pass, which is a positive integer.

中文字符串: 警报与设备异常相关参数
Chinese string: Alarm and equipment abnormality related parameters

中文字符串: 是否允许零位预警功能，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to allow the zero position warning function, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 警报与设备异常相关参数
Chinese string: Alarm and equipment abnormality related parameters

中文字符串: 零位预警比例，当零位变化大于 零点异常警报零点变化率阈值*此比例值 时发出警报，浮点数，取值范围：(0,1)。
Chinese string: Zero position warning ratio: when the zero position change is greater than the zero point abnormal alarm zero point change rate threshold * this ratio value, an alarm is issued. It is a floating point number with a value range of (0,1).

中文字符串: 警报与设备异常相关参数
Chinese string: Alarm and equipment abnormality related parameters

中文字符串: 是否允许启用新零位异常模式，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to enable the new zero position exception mode, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 警报与设备异常相关参数
Chinese string: Alarm and equipment abnormality related parameters

中文字符串: 在新零位异常模式下判定油箱温度异常的温度差异阈值，单位：摄氏度，浮点数。
Chinese string: The temperature difference threshold for determining fuel tank temperature abnormality in the new zero abnormality mode, in degrees Celsius, floating point number.

中文字符串: 警报与设备异常相关参数
Chinese string: Alarm and equipment abnormality related parameters

中文字符串: 在新零位异常模式下判定电离室温度异常的温度差异阈值，单位：摄氏度，浮点数。
Chinese string: The temperature difference threshold for determining ionization chamber temperature anomaly in the new zero anomaly mode, in degrees Celsius, floating point number.

中文字符串: 警报与设备异常相关参数
Chinese string: Alarm and equipment abnormality related parameters

中文字符串: 是否监控自动启停异常，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to monitor automatic start and stop abnormalities, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 警报与设备异常相关参数
Chinese string: Alarm and equipment abnormality related parameters

中文字符串: 自动启停超时判定超时分钟数，单位：分钟，浮点数，大于0。
Chinese string: Automatic start and stop timeout determination timeout minutes, unit: minute, floating point number, greater than 0.

中文字符串: 警报与设备异常相关参数
Chinese string: Alarm and equipment abnormality related parameters

中文字符串: 高度允许波动的最大值，单位：毫米，浮点数，应当大于0。
Chinese string: The maximum value of height fluctuation allowed, unit: mm, floating point number, should be greater than 0.

中文字符串: 警报与设备异常相关参数
Chinese string: Alarm and equipment abnormality related parameters

中文字符串: 高度警报边缘检测宽度，单位：毫米，浮点数，应当大于0。
Chinese string: Height alarm edge detection width, unit: mm, floating point number, should be greater than 0.

中文字符串: 警报与设备异常相关参数
Chinese string: Alarm and equipment abnormality related parameters

中文字符串: 高度警报边缘检测敏感度，浮点数，(0,1)。
Chinese string: High alarm edge detection sensitivity, floating point number, (0,1).

中文字符串: 警报与设备异常相关参数
Chinese string: Alarm and equipment abnormality related parameters

中文字符串: 高度警报边缘检测极差警报限值，单位：毫米，浮点数，应当大于0。
Chinese string: High alarm edge detection extreme alarm limit, unit: mm, floating point number, should be greater than 0.

中文字符串: 软件退出时是否自动关闭 XRay 发生器，是：True，否：False
Chinese string: Whether to automatically close the XRay generator when the software exits, yes: True, no: False

中文字符串: 数据监控重连时间，单位：秒
Chinese string: Data monitoring reconnection time, unit: seconds

中文字符串: 是否开启数据服务器，是：True,否：False
Chinese string: Whether to open the data server, yes: True, no: False

中文字符串: 是否开启通用外部通信接口，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to enable the universal external communication interface, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 每隔若干小时自动保存配置文件，单位：小时，浮点数。
Chinese string: Automatically save the configuration file every certain number of hours. Unit: hours, floating point number.

中文字符串: 软件启动后是否自动连接到设备，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to automatically connect to the device after the software is started, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 要延迟连接设备的秒数，由于应用启动时占用CPU运算量较大，可能造成设备管理器动作执行超时，故增加此设置，单位：秒
Chinese string: The number of seconds to delay connecting to the device. Since the application takes up a lot of CPU computing when starting, it may cause the device manager action to time out, so this setting is added. Unit: seconds

中文字符串: 软件数据处理性能降级警报系数，每秒处理的数据包 小于 应该处理的数据包数 * 此值 时在日志中发出警报，浮点数。
Chinese string: Software data processing performance degradation alarm factor. The number of packets processed per second is less than the number of packets that should be processed. * When this value is reached, an alarm is issued in the log. It is a floating point number.

中文字符串: 运动控制板断线重连时间间隔，单位：秒。假设配置为“30 30 45 60”，那么代表第一次重连间隔时间为30秒，第二次重连间隔时间为30秒，依次类推，从第四次起间隔时间均为60秒。
Chinese string: The time interval for reconnecting the motion control board after disconnection, in seconds. If the configuration is "30 30 45 60", it means that the first reconnection interval is 30 seconds, the second reconnection interval is 30 seconds, and so on. From the fourth time onwards, the interval is 60 seconds.

中文字符串: 正在涂布时是否允许修改寻边参数（修改寻边参数会先于提取边界执行），是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to allow modification of edge-finding parameters during coating (modification of edge-finding parameters will be performed before extracting boundaries), yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 当前正在涂布时是否允许提取边界（注意：即使修改寻边参数未开启，提取边界仍可能成功），是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to allow border extraction when coating is currently in progress (Note: even if the modification of edge-finding parameters is not enabled, border extraction may still be successful), Yes: True, No: False.

中文字符串: 是否开启演示模式，演示模式下模拟数据时会循环读取模拟数据，并且不输出数据文件，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to enable the demonstration mode. In the demonstration mode, the simulation data will be read in a loop and no data file will be output. Yes: True, No: False.

中文字符串: 保护动作最大尝试次数，正整数。
Chinese string: The maximum number of attempts for protection action, a positive integer.

中文字符串: 启动扫描前是否按需自动进行一次寻边操作？是：True，否：False。目前的自动寻边条件是更改过配方中与宽度有关的参数。
Chinese string: Do you want to automatically perform an edge search before starting scanning? Yes: True, No: False. The current automatic edge search condition is that the width-related parameters in the recipe have been changed.

中文字符串: 启动扫描前是否强制进行一次寻边操作？是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Do you want to force an edge search before starting scanning? Yes: True, No: False.

中文字符串: 软件启动后立刻开始记录新卷？是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Start recording a new volume immediately after software starts? Yes: True, No: False.

中文字符串: 处理宽度，一般代指设备真实光斑大小，单位：毫米。
Chinese string: Processing width generally refers to the actual spot size of the device, unit: millimeter.
Substrate edge peak search lower limit
Pole edge peak search lower limit
Single and double-sided peak search lower limit

中文字符串: 第一次高斯滤波-窗口大小（整数值）
Chinese string: First Gaussian filter - window size (integer value)

中文字符串: 第一次高斯滤波-标准差
设备特征参数，用于位置纠偏
Chinese string: Equipment characteristic parameters, used for position correction

中文字符串: 数据横向偏移，当此值为正时，正向趟向右偏，负向趟向左偏移，单位：毫米。
Chinese string: The data is offset horizontally. When this value is positive, the positive stroke deviates to the right, and the negative stroke deviates to the left. Unit: millimeter.

中文字符串: 原始分辨率，不建议修改，单位：毫米
Chinese string: Original resolution, not recommended to modify, unit: mm

中文字符串: 最小极片宽，单位：毫米，当极片宽度小于此值时，不进行增强处理。
Chinese string: Minimum pole piece width, unit: millimeter. When the pole piece width is smaller than this value, no enhancement processing is performed.

中文字符串: 特殊极片宽，单位：毫米，当极片宽度小于此值时，使用特殊极片宽度参数H代替参数H，此值应当大于最小极片宽。
Chinese string: Special pole piece width, unit: millimeter. When the pole piece width is less than this value, use the special pole piece width parameter H instead of parameter H. This value should be greater than the minimum pole piece width.

中文字符串: 参数H，边界点到涂布区的处理宽度，单位：毫米。
Chinese string: Parameter H, the processing width from the boundary point to the coating area, unit: millimeter.

中文字符串: 特殊极片宽度参数H，涂布区宽度过小时所用的参数H，单位：毫米。
Chinese string: Special pole piece width parameter H, parameter H used when the coating area width is too small, unit: millimeter.

中文字符串: 参数I，与加测试窄条时的修正宽度有关，单位：毫米，目前项目取值12（对应窄条宽度大于20毫米）。
Chinese string: Parameter I is related to the correction width when adding a narrow test strip. The unit is millimeter. The current value of the item is 12 (corresponding to a narrow strip width greater than 20 mm).

中文字符串: 峰宽限制，当峰宽小于此值时，不认为是一个独立的峰，单位：毫米，浮点数。
Chinese string: Peak width limit: when the peak width is smaller than this value, it is not considered as an independent peak. Unit: millimeter, floating point number.

中文字符串: 第二次高斯滤波窗口大小（整数值）
Chinese string: Second Gaussian filter window size (integer value)

中文字符串: 第二次高斯滤波标准差
Chinese string: The second Gaussian filter standard deviation

中文字符串: 参数E，值必须为1、2或4，值越大处理效果越好。
Chinese string: Parameter E, the value must be 1, 2 or 4. The larger the value, the better the processing effect.

中文字符串: 是否处理窄条（这个是做窄条实验时需要但对窄条部分做特殊处理，如在正常生产环境中，该选项应当关闭），是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to process narrow strips (this is necessary when doing narrow strip experiments, but special processing is required for the narrow strip part. For example, in a normal production environment, this option should be turned off), yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 对窄条区域进行特殊处理时需要向窄条边界两侧扩展的宽度，单位：毫米。
Chinese string: The width that needs to be extended on both sides of the narrow strip boundary when performing special processing on the narrow strip area, unit: millimeter.

中文字符串: 对窄条区域运用移动平均算法时，算法所用的窗口宽度，单位：毫米。
Chinese string: When applying the moving average algorithm to a narrow area, the window width used by the algorithm is in millimeters.
The first N-1 layers of wavelet scale coefficients

中文字符串: 最后一层小波比例系数
Chinese string: The last layer of wavelet scale coefficients
The first N-1 layers of wavelet threshold coefficients

中文字符串: 最后一层小波阈值系数
Chinese string: The last layer of wavelet threshold coefficients

中文字符串: 基材边缘过滤半径，单位：毫米
Chinese string: Substrate edge filter radius, unit: mm

中文字符串: 是否移除无意义点，是：True，否：False
Chinese string: Whether to remove meaningless points, yes: True, no: False

中文字符串: 无意义点下界值（面密度值，低于该值视为无意义）
Chinese string: The lower limit of meaningless points (surface density value, below which it is considered meaningless)

中文字符串: 涂布方向是否是霍尔开关型编码器，是：True，否：False
Chinese string: Whether the coating direction is a Hall switch encoder, yes: True, no: False

中文字符串: 是否总是使用Y方向进行数据分析，是：True，否：False
Chinese string: Whether to always use the Y direction for data analysis, yes: True, no: False

中文字符串: 完整削薄区过滤方法，重量：Weight，位置：Position
Chinese string: Complete skived area filtering method, weight: Weight, position: Position

中文字符串: 完整削薄区过滤因子（一个实数）\r\n    在过滤方法是重量时，代表从削薄区提取中间位置到结束位置所有的数据点的数据值不能小于 中心值*设定值。\r\n    在过滤方法是位置时，代表从削薄区提取位置起直到（结束位置+设定值宽度）范围内不能存在与提取位置不同的边界点类型
Chinese string: Complete thinning area filter factor (a real number)\r\n When the filter method is weight, it means that the data value of all data points from the middle position to the end position of the thinning area cannot be less than the center value * the set value. \r\n When the filter method is position, it means that there cannot be a boundary point type different from the extraction position in the range from the thinning area extraction position to (end position + set value width).

中文字符串: 是否允许自动检测极片边界点，是：True，否：False，该选项打开后在进行极片标定/校验时，会自动检测极片边界点用于自动寻边功能
Chinese string: Whether to allow automatic detection of pole piece boundary points, yes: True, no: False. When this option is turned on, the pole piece boundary points will be automatically detected for automatic edge finding during pole piece calibration/verification.

中文字符串: 是否需要过滤掉有效数据较少的分区，是：True，否：False
Chinese string: Do you need to filter out partitions with less valid data? Yes: True, No: False

中文字符串: 包含有小于多少毫米的有效数据的分区属于小分区，单位：毫米
Chinese string: The partition containing valid data smaller than a certain number of millimeters is a small partition. Unit: millimeters

中文字符串: 当两趟之间测量时间相差超过多少分钟后认为在该位置有一个停机位，单位：分钟，浮点数。
Chinese string: When the measured time difference between two trips exceeds a certain number of minutes, it is considered that there is a parking space at that location. Unit: minute, floating point number.

中文字符串:
判断受停机位影响的趟的计算方式：
    ByMeter, 按米数
    ByTrip, 趟趟数
Chinese string: Calculation method for determining trips affected by parking positions: ByMeter, ByTrip, ByMeter

中文字符串: 因停机导致测量受影响的米数半径，在这个范围内的扫描趟会被标记为受停机影响，单位：米，浮点数。
Chinese string: The radius in meters that the measurement is affected by the downtime. Scans within this range will be marked as affected by the downtime. Unit: meter, floating point number.

中文字符串: 因停机导致测量受影响的趟数半径，在这个范围内的扫描趟会被标记为受停机影响，单位：趟，自然数。举例：当此值为2时，以停机位趟为中心，该趟本身及其前面紧邻的两趟和后面紧邻的两趟，合计5趟将被标记为停机位受影响趟。
Chinese string: The radius of the number of trips affected by the shutdown. The scanned trips within this range will be marked as affected by the shutdown. Unit: trip, natural number. For example: when this value is 2, with the parking stand trip as the center, the trip itself and the two trips immediately before and after it, a total of 5 trips will be marked as affected by the parking stand.

中文字符串: 是否强制开启收集基材吸收值（在启用基材分离测量模式时，此选项没有意义），是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to force the collection of substrate absorption values to start (this option has no meaning when substrate separation measurement mode is enabled), yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 光斑半径大小，单位：毫米，浮点数。
Chinese string: The radius of the light spot, unit: mm, floating point number.

中文字符串: 是否允许开启第二次定向滤波功能，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to allow the second directional filtering function to be enabled, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 第二次定向高斯滤波脚本
第二次定向高斯滤波从边界点开始跳过的宽度，单位：毫米，浮点数。
Chinese string: The width that the second directional Gaussian filter skips from the boundary point, unit: millimeter, floating point number.

中文字符串: 智能分区模式版本，支持的所有版本如下：\r\n        V1 ATL专版仅支持此版本，不受此参数影响，第一版智能分区模式，自动纠偏和智能分区是独立的纠偏模式，更偏向实际测量结果的一种分区方法；\r\n        V2 第二版智能分区模式，自动纠偏和智能分区需要同时开启，是更偏向实际采样校验的一种分区方法；
Chinese string: Smart partition mode version, all supported versions are as follows:\r\n V1 ATL special version only supports this version, not affected by this parameter, the first version of smart partition mode, automatic correction and smart partition are independent correction modes, a partition method that is more biased towards actual measurement results;\r\n V2 second version of smart partition mode, automatic correction and smart partition need to be turned on at the same time, which is a partition method that is more biased towards actual sampling verification;

中文字符串: 是否开启自动纠偏模式，注意：自动纠偏模式仅支持连续涂布模式。是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to enable the automatic correction mode. Note: the automatic correction mode only supports the continuous coating mode. Yes: True, No: False.

中文字符串: 是否开启智能分区模式，仅支持连续涂布模式，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to enable the intelligent partitioning mode, only supports the continuous coating mode, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: V1版智能分区模式下是否自动调整削薄区剔除宽度（各膜区宽度大致均相等时生效），是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: In the V1 version intelligent partitioning mode, whether to automatically adjust the thinning area rejection width (effective when the widths of each film area are roughly equal), yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 是否允许开启减本底功能，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to enable the background reduction function, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 减本底功能模式 ：\r\n    Static， 减静态本底（使用运动控制板采集的本底信号）\r\n    Dynamic，动态减本底（使用软件采集的不同温度对应不同本底信号）
Chinese string: Background reduction function mode: Static, static background reduction (background signal collected by motion control board) Dynamic, dynamic background reduction (different background signals corresponding to different temperatures collected by software)

中文字符串: 开启记录本底信号多少秒后才真正记录本底信号，单位：秒，自然数。
Chinese string: How many seconds will it take for the background signal to be actually recorded after the background signal is recorded, unit: seconds, natural number.

中文字符串: 当电离室温度高于多少度时，允许剔除本底信号，单位：摄氏度，浮点数。
Chinese string: When the ionization chamber temperature is higher than a certain degree, the background signal can be eliminated. Unit: Celsius, floating point number.

中文字符串: 是否开启实时削薄区剔除功能（实验性质，仅支持连续涂布模式），是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to enable the real-time thinning area removal function (experimental, only supports continuous coating mode), yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 当发生需要跳过数据的异常时，是否要过滤掉整趟数据，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: When an exception occurs that requires data to be skipped, whether to filter out the entire trip of data, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 最大允许积压的趟数据处理的趟数，正整数。
Chinese string: The maximum number of backlogs allowed for data processing, a positive integer.

中文字符串: 限制原始/静态数据记录的真实分辨率，大于0时有效，单位：毫秒，值越大分辨率越差，统计结果越好。
Chinese string: Limit the real resolution of raw/static data records. It is effective when it is greater than 0. The unit is milliseconds. The larger the value, the worse the resolution and the better the statistical results.

中文字符串: 生成设备校验报告时所使用的分析方法，注意，这个选项对界面的“正反校验”功能无效：\r\n    ExtremeDifference, 使用正负向极差，更严格\r\n    AverageDifference, 使用正负向求均之后的差值，稍宽松
Chinese string: The analysis method used when generating the equipment verification report. Note that this option is invalid for the "positive and negative verification" function of the interface:\r\n ExtremeDifference, using the positive and negative extremes, more stringent\r\n AverageDifference, using the difference after averaging the positive and negative values, slightly looser

中文字符串: 距离传感器数据高斯宽度，自然数。
Chinese string: The Gaussian width of the distance sensor data, a natural number.

中文字符串: 距离传感器数据高斯标准差，浮点数，正数。
Chinese string: Gaussian standard deviation of distance sensor data, floating point number, positive number.
Ray channel coefficient K, floating point number.
Ray channel coefficient B, floating point number.

中文字符串: 是否允许使用时序横向EWMA算法，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to allow the use of the time series horizontal EWMA algorithm, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 时序横向EWMA算法系数a，Yn=Xn*a+Xn-1'*(1-a)，浮点数，[0,1]，值为1时相当于关闭算法。
Chinese string: Time series horizontal EWMA algorithm coefficient a, Yn=Xn*a+Xn-1'*(1-a), floating point number, [0,1]. A value of 1 is equivalent to turning off the algorithm.

中文字符串: 是否开启射线通道差值滤波，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to enable ray channel difference filtering, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 射线通道差值滤波次数，正整数。
Chinese string: The number of ray channel difference filtering, a positive integer.

中文字符串:
值过滤方式：
    Normal, 常规方案，这种方案下以公差倍数定义下限，以固定值定义上限
    Percent, 百分比方案，这种方案以基准值的上下比率分别定义过滤上限和下限
Chinese string: Value filtering method: Normal, conventional scheme, in which the lower limit is defined by the tolerance multiple and the upper limit is defined by a fixed value Percent, percentage scheme, in which the upper and lower limits of the filter are defined by the upper and lower ratios of the reference value

中文字符串: 是否存在三温（上空气温度、极片温度、下空气温度）传感器，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether there is a three-temperature (upper air temperature, pole piece temperature, lower air temperature) sensor, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 在发生器类型为BetaRay且存在三温传感器时，该参数有效，是否允许启用温度补偿功能，是：True，否：False
Chinese string: When the generator type is BetaRay and there are three temperature sensors, this parameter is valid. Whether to enable the temperature compensation function, yes: True, no: False

中文字符串: 上层空气厚度，单位：毫米
下层空气厚度，单位：毫米
合法的最低温度值，当采集温度低于此值时，数据将被跳过，单位：摄氏度
Chinese string: The legal minimum temperature value. When the collected temperature is lower than this value, the data will be skipped. Unit: Celsius

中文字符串: 是否开启温补实验窗口，是：True，否：False，该参数仅在温补功能开启时起作用。
Chinese string: Whether to open the temperature compensation experiment window, yes: True, no: False. This parameter only works when the temperature compensation function is turned on.

中文字符串: 温补零位跟踪位置相对极片原点侧边界再向原点方向偏移多少距离，单位：毫米
