Chinese string: How much is the temperature compensation zero tracking position offset from the side boundary of the pole piece origin to the origin direction? Unit: mm

中文字符串: 温补预热时间，单位：分钟，浮点数，如：5.5，代表五分半钟，该值不能设为0。
Chinese string: Warm-up preheating time, unit: minute, floating point number, such as: 5.5, represents five and a half minutes, this value cannot be set to 0.

中文字符串: 是否允许输出三温度文件，是：True，否：False，该参数仅在存在三温传感器时有效。
Chinese string: Whether to allow the output of three-temperature files, yes: True, no: False. This parameter is only valid when there is a three-temperature sensor.

中文字符串: 是否有标准片采集设备，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether there is a standard film acquisition device, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 标准片所在起始坐标，单位：毫米，浮点数。
Chinese string: The starting coordinates of the standard film, unit: mm, floating point number.

中文字符串: 标准片所在结束坐标，单位：毫米，浮点数。
Chinese string: The ending coordinates of the standard film, unit: mm, floating point number.

中文字符串: 标准片日志文件最大保存个数，自然数，此值为零时代表不设置保存个数上限。
Chinese string: The maximum number of standard slice log files that can be saved is a natural number. When this value is zero, it means that there is no upper limit on the number of saved files.

中文字符串: 标准片EWMA权重系数，浮点数，合理范围为0-1，默认值为0.9，值为0时相当于关闭算法。
Chinese string: Standard film EWMA weight coefficient, floating point number, reasonable range is 0-1, the default value is 0.9, and a value of 0 is equivalent to turning off the algorithm.

中文字符串: 标准片吸收值补偿系数，默认值为 1，浮点数。
Chinese string: The standard film absorption value compensation coefficient, the default value is 1, floating point number.

中文字符串: 标准片变化限值，ln后的数值，浮点数。
Chinese string: Standard film variation limit, value after ln, floating point number.
Whether there is a marker, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 打标器与射线束的距离，打标器在射线束的远原点方向为正值，否则为负值（单位：毫米）
Chinese string: The distance between the marker and the beam. The distance is positive when the marker is in the far direction of the beam, otherwise it is negative (unit: mm)

中文字符串: 自动打标安全区宽度（打标必须在极片边界再向内缩安全区宽度才允许，单位：毫米）
Chinese string: Automatic marking safety zone width (marking must be within the electrode boundary and then retracted to the safety zone width before it is allowed, unit: mm)

中文字符串: 标定时是否允许提示自动打标，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to allow automatic marking prompt during calibration, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 校验时是否允许提示自动打标，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to allow automatic marking prompt during verification, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 当连接设备后自动重置扩展输出状态，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Automatically reset the extended output status when a device is connected, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 是否存在清洁/吹扫装置，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether a cleaning/purging device exists, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 吹气清洁/吹扫最大可设置时间（防止意外设置过大值，单位：秒）
Chinese string: Maximum settable time for air cleaning/purging (to prevent accidental setting of excessive value, unit: seconds)

中文字符串: 是否根据换向时间自动调节清洁/吹扫秒数，是：True，否：False。（如果为否，则使用 AutoCleanSeconds 参数作为清洁/吹扫秒数）
Chinese string: Whether to automatically adjust the cleaning/purge seconds according to the switching time, yes: True, no: False. (If no, use the AutoCleanSeconds parameter as the cleaning/purge seconds)

中文字符串: 自动清洁/吹扫秒数，单位：秒，浮点数。
Chinese string: Automatic cleaning/purging seconds, unit: seconds, floating point number.

中文字符串: 当前探测器位置小于多少时进行吹扫，单位：毫米，浮点数。
Chinese string: The current detector position must be less than what value before purging begins. Unit: millimeter, floating point number.

中文字符串: 是否仅在设备空闲时（没有任何任务）时进行吹扫，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to purge only when the device is idle (no tasks), yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 每隔多少周期进行一次自动清洁/吹扫，单位：周期，整数。
Chinese string: How often do you perform automatic cleaning/purging? Unit: cycle, integer.

中文字符串: 冷却水控制器和温湿度监控器共用Com口名称。
Chinese string: The cooling water controller and the temperature and humidity monitor share the same Com port name.

中文字符串: 是否存在冷却水控制器，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether there is a cooling water controller, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 是否存在温湿度传感器，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether there is a temperature and humidity sensor, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 温湿度监控器读取周期，每多少秒读取一次数据，单位：秒，浮点数。
Chinese string: The reading cycle of the temperature and humidity monitor, how often the data is read, unit: seconds, floating point number.

中文字符串: 温湿度监控预警值，单位：摄氏度，浮点数。
Chinese string: Temperature and humidity monitoring warning value, unit: Celsius, floating point number.

中文字符串: 水冷日志最大保留天数，超过此天数的日志将被自动清除，当该值小于等于0时不起作用。
Chinese string: The maximum number of days for water cooling logs to be retained. Logs exceeding this number of days will be automatically cleared. When the value is less than or equal to 0, it has no effect.

中文字符串: 当使用Tec协议时，是否真实存在Tec设备，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: When using the Tec protocol, whether the Tec device actually exists, yes: True, no: False.
Whether to use the IO board, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串:
IO板通讯参数，IO板支持通过串口或者网口进行通讯。
    串口参数格式：站号, Serial, Com端口名称, 波特率, 奇偶性（None/Odd/Even）, 数据位, 停止位(0/1/2/1.5)，例如：1, Serial, Com3, 57600, Even, 8, 1
    网口参数格式：站号, Tcp, IP地址:端口号，例如：1, Tcp, 192.168.0.7:8081
Chinese string: IO board communication parameters, IO board supports communication through serial port or network port. Serial port parameter format: station number, Serial, Com port name, baud rate, parity (None/Odd/Even), data bit, stop bit (0/1/2/1.5), for example: 1, Serial, Com3, 57600, Even, 8, 1 Network port parameter format: station number, Tcp, IP address: port number, for example: 1, Tcp, 192.168.0.7:8081

中文字符串: 当使用Tec2协议时，是否真实存在Tec2设备，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: When using the Tec2 protocol, whether the Tec2 device actually exists, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 是否使用了距离传感器，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether the distance sensor is used, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 距离传感器有效范围起始值，单位：mA，浮点数。
Chinese string: The starting value of the effective range of the distance sensor, unit: mA, floating point number.

中文字符串: 距离传感器有效范围截止值，单位：mA，浮点数。
Chinese string: Distance sensor effective range cutoff value, unit: mA, floating point number.

中文字符串: 高度测量装置（距离传感器通道1）与光斑中心距离设定，装在光斑中心的远原点方向为正，否则为负，单位：毫米，浮点数。
Chinese string: The distance between the height measuring device (distance sensor channel 1) and the center of the light spot is set. If it is installed in the center of the light spot, the direction far from the origin is positive, otherwise it is negative. Unit: mm, floating point number.

中文字符串: 距离传感器1的比例系数，浮点数。
Chinese string: The scaling factor of distance sensor 1, floating point number.

中文字符串: 距离传感器1的平移系数，浮点数。
Chinese string: Translation coefficient of distance sensor 1, floating point number.

中文字符串: 涂布跟随最大允许的扫描速度，单位：毫米/秒，浮点数。
Chinese string: The maximum allowed scanning speed of coating follower, unit: mm/s, floating point number.

中文字符串: 涂布跟随最小允许的扫描速度，单位：毫米/秒，浮点数。
Chinese string: The minimum allowed scanning speed for coating. Unit: mm/s, floating point number.

中文字符串: 涂布跟随调整扫描速度时的步长（即每次调整扫描速度的调节量），单位：毫米/秒，浮点数。
Chinese string: The step length when coating follows the adjustment of scanning speed (i.e. the adjustment amount of scanning speed each time), unit: mm/s, floating point number.

中文字符串: 一周期扫描时间对应的涂布长度允许的最小值，单位：米，浮点数。
Chinese string: The minimum allowed coating length corresponding to one cycle scanning time, unit: meter, floating point number.

中文字符串: 自动调整扫描速度的保护时间，在这个时间内不监测涂布速度，防止重复设置扫描速度，单位：秒，整数。
Chinese string: The protection time for automatically adjusting the scanning speed. During this time, the coating speed is not monitored to prevent repeated setting of the scanning speed. Unit: seconds, integer.

中文字符串: 调整速度时的模式，支持的模式如下：\r\n        DirectWrite, 在运动过程中直接写入（耗时短，但是可能导致运动控制板失控）\r\n        StopWriteStart, 先停止扫描停止后写入扫描速度，之后再启动扫描（耗时长，但是不太可能导致运动控制板失控）
Chinese string: The modes for adjusting the speed are as follows:\r\n DirectWrite, write directly during motion (short time, but may cause the motion control board to lose control)\r\n StopWriteStart, stop scanning first, then write the scanning speed, and then restart scanning (long time, but less likely to cause the motion control board to lose control)

中文字符串: 涂布速度每秒异常变化率，单位：毫米/秒，浮点数。
Chinese string: Abnormal change rate of coating speed per second, unit: mm/s, floating point number.

中文字符串: 寻边跟踪功能需满足分析的趟数
Chinese string: The edge tracking function must meet the number of passes analyzed

中文字符串: 寻边跟踪自动放宽起始放宽宽度，单位：毫米，浮点数。
Chinese string: The starting relaxation width of automatic relaxation for edge tracking, unit: mm, floating point number.

中文字符串: 寻边跟踪自动放宽宽度最大值，单位：毫米，浮点数。
Chinese string: The maximum value of the automatic relaxation width for edge tracking, unit: mm, floating point number.

中文字符串: 寻边跟踪忽略偏移量，单位：毫米，如果寻边跟踪检测到与上次找到的边界点位置相差小于此值，寻边跟踪将会停止修正扫描区间，仅更新软件内部基材膜区边界缓存。
Chinese string: Edge tracking ignores the offset, unit: mm. If the edge tracking detects that the position of the boundary point found last time is less than this value, the edge tracking will stop correcting the scanning interval and only update the software's internal substrate film area boundary cache.

中文字符串: 寻边跟踪宽度异常警报允许最大误差，单位：毫米，浮点数。
Chinese string: The maximum allowable error of the edge tracking width abnormal alarm, unit: mm, floating point number.

中文字符串: 当设置扫描区间的时候是否允许先停止扫描后再设置参数，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: When setting the scanning interval, is it allowed to stop scanning first and then set parameters? Yes: True, No: False.

中文字符串: 当无法找到基材边时是否自动扩展扫描宽度？是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Automatically expand the scan width when the substrate edge cannot be found? Yes: True, No: False.

中文字符串: 基材分离测量模式参数
是否使用基材分离测量模式（超薄极片模式），在该模式下，认为基材吸收值是动态变化的，并且基材重与涂层重将分别标定与计算，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to use the substrate separation measurement mode (ultra-thin electrode mode). In this mode, the substrate absorption value is considered to be dynamically changing, and the substrate weight and coating weight will be calibrated and calculated separately. Yes: True, No: False.

中文字符串: 基材分离测量模式参数
是否使用更加严格的基材分离测量模式，该模式下，认为基材重是动态变化的，是：Ture，否：False。注意与IsUseSubstrateSeparateMeasuringMode做区分，这两个是独立互斥的功能（但共用一些参数），只能在同一时间开启其中一种测量模式。
Chinese string: Whether to use a more stringent substrate separation measurement mode, in which the substrate weight is considered to be dynamically changing. Yes: True, No: False. Note that this is different from IsUseSubstrateSeparateMeasuringMode, as these two are independent and mutually exclusive functions (but share some parameters), and only one of these measurement modes can be enabled at the same time.

中文字符串: 基材分离测量模式参数

Chinese string: Base material calibration K value, floating point number.

中文字符串: 基材分离测量模式参数

Chinese string: Base material calibration B value, floating point number.

中文字符串: 基材分离测量模式参数
计算基材吸收值或动态基材重时所用参考的趟数，整型。
Chinese string: The reference pass number used when calculating substrate absorption value or dynamic substrate weight, integer.

中文字符串: 基材分离测量模式参数
基材标准差限值，浮点数。
Chinese string: The base material standard deviation limit, a floating point number.

中文字符串: 基材分离测量模式参数
基材重均重偏差限值，浮点数。
Chinese string: The average weight deviation limit of the substrate weight, a floating point number.

中文字符串: 基材分离测量模式参数
基材警报判断趟数，正整数。
Chinese string: The number of times the substrate alarm is judged, a positive integer.

中文字符串: 基材分离测量模式参数
基材分离测量模式（超薄极片模式）管电压，单位：伏特，浮点数，留空不起作用。
Chinese string: Tube voltage in substrate separation measurement mode (ultra-thin electrode mode), unit: volt, floating point number, leaving it blank will have no effect.

中文字符串: 基材分离测量模式参数
基材分离测量模式（超薄极片模式）管电流，单位：微安，浮点数，留空不起作用。
Chinese string: Tube current in substrate separation measurement mode (ultra-thin electrode mode), unit: microampere, floating point number, leaving it blank will have no effect.

中文字符串: 是否允许开启横向N点平滑算法进行滤波，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to enable the horizontal N-point smoothing algorithm for filtering, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 参与一次平滑运算的数据点的一阶差分序列的上限，即要求参与平滑运算的相邻两个数据值不能差异太大，如果大于等于此上限则放弃此次滤波运算，保持数据原始值。此参数仅应用于横向N点平滑。
Chinese string: The upper limit of the first-order difference sequence of the data points involved in a smoothing operation, that is, the difference between the two adjacent data values involved in the smoothing operation cannot be too large. If it is greater than or equal to this upper limit, the filtering operation is abandoned and the original data value is kept. This parameter is only applied to horizontal N-point smoothing.

中文字符串: 横向平滑系数数组，定义每个点由多少个点计算而来及权重系数，浮点数。
Chinese string: Array of horizontal smoothing coefficients, defining how many points each point is calculated from and the weight coefficient, floating point number.

中文字符串: 是否允许使用横向滤波算法2（膜区均值+系数），是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to allow the use of lateral filtering algorithm 2 (membrane area mean + coefficient), yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 横向滤波算法2（膜区均值+系数）系数，浮点数，(0,1]
Chinese string: Transverse filtering algorithm 2 (membrane area mean + coefficient) coefficient, floating point number, (0,1]

中文字符串: 是否允许使用横向滤波算法3（膜区多项式趋势+系数），是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to allow the use of lateral filtering algorithm 3 (membrane area polynomial trend + coefficient), yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 横向滤波算法3（膜区多项式趋势+系数）多项式次方数，正整数
Chinese string: Transverse filtering algorithm 3 (membrane area polynomial trend + coefficient) polynomial power, positive integer

中文字符串: 横向滤波算法3（膜区多项式趋势+系数）系数，原值占比，浮点数，[0,1]
Chinese string: Transverse filtering algorithm 3 (membrane area polynomial trend + coefficient) coefficient, original value ratio, floating point number, [0,1]

中文字符串: 是否允许开启纵向N点平滑算法进行滤波，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to enable the vertical N-point smoothing algorithm for filtering, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 参与一次平滑运算的数据点的极差的上限，即要求参与平滑运算的数据值不能波动太大，如果大于等于此上限则放弃此次滤波运算，保持数据原始值。此参数应用于纵向N点平滑和纵向单值滤波。
Chinese string: The upper limit of the range of the data points involved in a smoothing operation, that is, the data value involved in the smoothing operation should not fluctuate too much. If it is greater than or equal to this upper limit, the filtering operation is abandoned and the original data value is maintained. This parameter is applied to longitudinal N-point smoothing and longitudinal single-value filtering.

中文字符串: 纵向N点平滑的权值数组，每个<double>代表一趟数据对应位置的权值，第一个元素代表离当前趟最远的一趟的权值。有几个元素就有几趟的数据参与运算（包含当前趟），趟数为偶数时效果最好。
Chinese string: The weight array of N-point vertical smoothing, each <double> represents the weight of a trip corresponding to the position, the first element represents the weight of the trip farthest from the current trip. There are as many elements as there are trips of data involved in the calculation (including the current trip), and the best effect is when the number of trips is an even number.

中文字符串: 在涂布时，是否允许开启纵向N点平滑算法进行滤波，是：True，否：False。注意，仅在开启纵向平滑时该参数才有效，不区分是否削薄区数据。
Chinese string: During coating, whether to enable the longitudinal N-point smoothing algorithm for filtering, yes: True, no: False. Note that this parameter is only valid when longitudinal smoothing is enabled, regardless of whether the thinning area data is used.

中文字符串: 是否允许开启提取削薄区用纵向N点平滑算法进行滤波，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to enable the extraction of thinning areas and filter them using the longitudinal N-point smoothing algorithm, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 提取削薄区用纵向N点平滑的权值数组，每个<double>代表一趟数据对应位置的权值，第一个元素代表离当前趟最远的一趟的权值。有几个元素就有几趟的数据参与运算（包含当前趟）。
Chinese string: Extract the thinning area using the weight array of N vertical points smoothing. Each <double> represents the weight of a data position. The first element represents the weight of the farthest data from the current data. The number of elements is the number of data involved in the calculation (including the current data).

中文字符串: 削薄区参与一次平滑运算的数据点的极差的上限，即要求参与平滑运算的数据值不能波动太大，如果大于等于此上限则放弃此次滤波运算，保持数据原始值。此参数应用于纵向N点平滑和纵向单值滤波。
Chinese string: The upper limit of the range of the data points in the thinning area that participate in a smoothing operation, that is, the data value participating in the smoothing operation should not fluctuate too much. If it is greater than or equal to this upper limit, the filtering operation is abandoned and the original data value is maintained. This parameter is applied to longitudinal N-point smoothing and longitudinal single-value filtering.

中文字符串: 是否允许使用纵向单值滤波算法，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to allow the use of longitudinal single-value filtering algorithm, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 纵向单值滤波算法系数，该系数应用于单值，浮点数，[0,1)
Chinese string: Vertical single-value filtering algorithm coefficient, this coefficient is applied to a single value, floating point number, [0,1)

中文字符串: 是否允许使用削薄区纵向单值滤波算法，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to allow the use of the thinning zone longitudinal single-value filtering algorithm, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 削薄区纵向单值滤波算法系数，该系数应用于单值，浮点数，[0,1)
Chinese string: The coefficient of the longitudinal single-value filtering algorithm in the thinning area. This coefficient is applied to a single value, floating point number, [0,1)

中文字符串: 全局EWMA算法系数，值为1时代表不进行修正，值越大响应性越好，稳定性越差，取值范围：(0,1]，值为1时相当于关闭算法。
Chinese string: Global EWMA algorithm coefficient. When the value is 1, no correction is performed. The larger the value, the better the responsiveness and the worse the stability. The value range is: (0,1]. When the value is 1, it is equivalent to turning off the algorithm.

中文字符串: 全局移动平均算法窗口，自然数，值为0时代表不进行修正。
Chinese string: Global moving average algorithm window, a natural number. A value of 0 means no correction.

中文字符串: 是否允许开启定向滤波功能，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to enable the directional filtering function, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 定向高斯滤波脚本，每个膜区一个高斯函数，用分号隔开，例如：gauss(21,1.6);gauss(21,1.6);gauss(21,1.6)。
Chinese string: Directed Gaussian filtering script, one Gaussian function for each membrane region, separated by semicolons, for example: gauss(21,1.6);gauss(21,1.6);gauss(21,1.6).

中文字符串: 参与运算的一个膜区原始信号的极差不能大于此值，否则本膜区不进行高斯滤波处理。
Chinese string: The range of the original signal of a membrane area involved in the operation cannot be greater than this value, otherwise the Gaussian filtering process will not be performed on this membrane area.

中文字符串: 定向高斯滤波从边界点开始跳过的宽度，单位：毫米，浮点数。
Chinese string: The width of the directional Gaussian filter that is skipped from the boundary point, unit: mm, floating point number.

中文字符串: 是否允许实时数据EWMA处理？是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Allow real-time data EWMA processing? Yes: True, No: False.

中文字符串: 实时数据EWMA处理系数，浮点数，(0,1]，值为1时相当于关闭算法。
Chinese string: Real-time data EWMA processing coefficient, floating point number, (0,1]. A value of 1 is equivalent to turning off the algorithm.

中文字符串:
激光器类型：
  None 不存在，没有安装激光器
  Normal 正常，与探测器发生器一起运动的激光器
  Fixed 固定，安装在一个固定测量位置的激光器
Chinese string: Laser Type: None None, no laser installed Normal Normal, a laser that moves with the detector generator Fixed Fixed, a laser installed in a fixed measurement position

中文字符串:
运动控制器类型，可选择以下设备：
    Tgdamc， 运动控制板
    Mcda， 新运动控制板
Chinese string: Motion controller type, you can choose the following devices: Tgdamc, motion control board Mcda, new motion control board

中文字符串:
射线通道数据源，可选择以下数据源之一：
    Tgdamc1Ray， 运动控制板1的射线通道
    Tgdamc1Laser1， 运动控制板1的激光1通道
    Tgdamc1Laser2， 运动控制板1的激光2通道
    Tgdamc2Ray， 运动控制板2的射线通道
    Tgdamc2Laser1， 运动控制板2的激光1通道
    Tgdamc2Laser2， 运动控制板2的激光2通道
    FpgaValue1， Fpga板卡的信号1

    McdaSeparateValue， Mcda板卡激光头拆分信号

中文字符串:
当设备为一体机设备时，优先使用的数据通道（或称主通道），某些功能，如，设置启动扫描区间，需要给定以哪个数据通道的数据为参数，可以选择以下数据通道：

Some functions, such as setting the start scanning interval, need to specify the data of which data channel as a parameter. The following data channels can be selected: Ray, ray data channel Laser, laser data channel

中文字符串: 当信号源含有来自多个传感器数据时，要求设备设置扫描区间时要确保多传感器信号融合时有多少毫米的数据是重合的，单位：毫米，浮点数。
Chinese string: When the signal source contains data from multiple sensors, the device is required to set the scanning interval to ensure how many millimeters of data overlap when the multi-sensor signals are fused. Unit: millimeter, floating point number.

中文字符串:
运动控制板协议版本，目前包含以下版本：
        V1, 适用于20190919之前生产的运动控制板
        V2, 对应运动控制板第二代版本，支持多架功能
        V2Laser, 对应运动控制板第二代激光版本，支持多架功能，支持射线+激光双4K数据传输速率
        V3, 对应运动控制板第三代版本，支持40K激光数据传输速率
        V4, 对应运动控制板第四代版本，支持50K激光+射线数据传输速率
Chinese string:
The motion control board protocol version currently includes the following versions:
 V1, applicable to motion control boards produced before 20190919
 V2, corresponding to the second generation version of the motion control board, supports multi-frame function
 V2Laser, corresponding to the second generation laser version of the motion control board, supports multi-frame function, supports ray + laser dual 4K data transmission rate
 V3, corresponding to the third generation version of the motion control board, supports 40K laser data transmission rate
 V4, corresponding to the fourth generation version of the motion control board, supports 50K laser + ray data transmission rate

中文字符串: 设备支持的扩展设备功能，目前包含以下功能（每项功能以英文“,”号隔开）：\r\n        Tec， 支持TEC功能，即发生器温控装置；\r\n        AdvancedLightSoundControl， 支持高级声光控制功能，高级声光控制功能需要与运动控制板程序对应，不可随意修改；
Chinese string: The extended device functions supported by the device currently include the following functions (each function is separated by an English ","):\r\n Tec, supports TEC function, i.e., generator temperature control device;\r\n AdvancedLightSoundControl, supports advanced sound and light control function. The advanced sound and light control function needs to correspond to the motion control board program and cannot be modified at will;

中文字符串: 第二运动控制板原始数据保留天数
Chinese string: Second motion control board original data retention days

中文字符串: 第二运动控制板原始数据保存位置（留空使用默认路径“%LocalAppData%\\KFCKDevices\\Pure2”，如需自定义路径，则要求该路径必须为绝对路径，如：D:\\RawData，且需确保该文件夹已存在）
Chinese string: The location where the raw data of the second motion control board is saved (leave it blank to use the default path "%LocalAppData%\\KFCKDevices\\Pure2". If you need to customize the path, the path must be an absolute path, such as: D:\\RawData, and make sure that the folder already exists)

中文字符串: FPGA板卡采集频率，单位：Hz，合理范围为100-200000。
Chinese string: FPGA board acquisition frequency, unit: Hz, the reasonable range is 100-200000.

中文字符串: FPGA板卡数据扫描周期（估计值），单位：毫秒，正整数，即大概每多少毫秒从板卡缓存读取一次数据。
Chinese string: FPGA board data scanning period (estimated value), unit: milliseconds, positive integer, that is, how often data is read from the board cache.

中文字符串: FPGA旋转编码器（X方向）周脉冲数，正整数。
Chinese string: FPGA rotary encoder (X direction) pulse number per cycle, a positive integer.

中文字符串: FPGA旋转编码器（X方向）周长，单位：毫米，浮点数。
Chinese string: FPGA rotary encoder (X direction) circumference, unit: mm, floating point number.

中文字符串: FPGA探测器编码器（Y方向）周脉冲数，正整数。
Chinese string: FPGA detector encoder (Y direction) pulse number per week, a positive integer.

中文字符串: FPGA探测器编码器（Y方向）周长，单位：毫米，浮点数。
Chinese string: FPGA detector encoder (Y direction) circumference, unit: mm, floating point number.

中文字符串: 是否开启编码器Z信号复位X坐标功能，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to enable the encoder Z signal reset X coordinate function, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串:
X 方向编码器工作模式，所有支持的工作模式如下：
    None， 无计数器；
    Mode1X， 编码器 1x 计数模式；
    Mode2X， 编码器 2x 计数模式；
    Mode4X， 编码器 4x 计数模式。

Y 方向编码器工作模式，所有支持的工作模式如下：
    None， 无计数器；
    Mode1X， 编码器 1x 计数模式；
    Mode2X， 编码器 2x 计数模式；
    Mode4X， 编码器 4x 计数模式。
是否开启Fpga板Y坐标容错机制，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to enable the Fpga board Y coordinate fault tolerance mechanism, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: FpgaY坐标容错点数，即允许连续出现错误坐标点数的上限，正整数。
Chinese string: The number of FpgaY coordinate error tolerance points, that is, the upper limit of the number of consecutive error coordinate points allowed, a positive integer.

中文字符串: FpgaY坐标容错参考点数，即处于错误坐标点两侧的正确点数（参数本身为单侧的点数），用于为判定错误点做参考，正整数，大于等于2。
Chinese string: The number of FpgaY coordinate error tolerance reference points, that is, the number of correct points on both sides of the error coordinate point (the parameter itself is the number of points on one side), is used as a reference for determining the error point. It is a positive integer greater than or equal to 2.

中文字符串: Fpga原始数据保存位置（留空使用默认路径“%LocalAppData%\\KFCKDevices\\Fpga”，如需自定义路径，则要求该路径必须为绝对路径，如：D:\\RawData，且需确保该文件夹已存在）
Chinese string: Fpga raw data save location (leave it blank to use the default path "%LocalAppData%\\KFCKDevices\\Fpga". If you need to customize the path, the path must be an absolute path, such as: D:\\RawData, and make sure the folder already exists)

中文字符串:
Mcda协议版本：
    V1， 最初始的协议版本
    V2， 支持多架的 MCDA 版本
Chinese string: Mcda protocol version: V1, the initial protocol version V2, supports multiple MCDA versions

中文字符串: Mcda原始数据保存位置（留空使用默认路径“%LocalAppData%\\KFCKDevices\\Mcda”，如需自定义路径，则要求该路径必须为绝对路径，如：D:\\RawData，且需确保该文件夹已存在）
Chinese string: Mcda raw data save location (leave it blank to use the default path "%LocalAppData%\\KFCKDevices\\Mcda". If you need to customize the path, the path must be an absolute path, such as: D:\\RawData, and make sure the folder exists)

中文字符串: Mcda旋转编码器（X方向）周脉冲数，正整数。
Chinese string: Mcda rotary encoder (X direction) pulse number per week, positive integer.

中文字符串: Mcda旋转编码器（X方向）周长，单位：毫米，浮点数。
Chinese string: Mcda rotary encoder (X direction) circumference, unit: mm, floating point number.

中文字符串: Mcda探测器编码器（Y方向）周脉冲数，正整数。
Chinese string: Mcda detector encoder (Y direction) pulse number per week, a positive integer.

中文字符串: Mcda探测器编码器（Y方向）周长，单位：毫米，浮点数。
Chinese string: Mcda detector encoder (Y direction) circumference, unit: mm, floating point number.

中文字符串: Mcda电机（Y方向）周脉冲数，正整数。
Chinese string: Mcda motor (Y direction) pulse number per cycle, a positive integer.

中文字符串: Mcda电机（Y方向）周长，单位：毫米，浮点数。
Chinese string: Mcda motor (Y direction) circumference, unit: mm, floating point number.

中文字符串: Mcda探测器编码器（Y2方向）周脉冲数，正整数。
Chinese string: Mcda detector encoder (Y2 direction) pulse number per week, a positive integer.

中文字符串: Mcda探测器编码器（Y2方向）周长，单位：毫米，浮点数。
Chinese string: Mcda detector encoder (Y2 direction) circumference, unit: mm, floating point number.

中文字符串: Mcda电机（Y2方向）周脉冲数，正整数。
Chinese string: The number of pulses per cycle of Mcda motor (Y2 direction), a positive integer.

中文字符串: Mcda电机（Y2方向）周长，单位：毫米，浮点数。
Chinese string: Mcda motor (Y2 direction) circumference, unit: mm, floating point number.

中文字符串: MCDA设备启动扫描前的默认复位长度，单位：毫米，浮点数。
Chinese string: The default reset length of the MCDA device before starting scanning, unit: mm, floating point number.

中文字符串: MCDA设备数据信号1的信号值放大倍率，大于0的浮点数，默认为1，即原值输出。
Chinese string: The signal value magnification of the MCDA device data signal 1, a floating point number greater than 0, the default is 1, that is, the original value is output.

中文字符串: Mcda设备开关Beta放射源超时时间，单位：秒，浮点数。
Chinese string: Mcda device switch Beta radiation source timeout, unit: second, floating point number.

中文字符串: 后台服务端口号，非常重要，前台界面启动后会从后台服务获取数据。
Chinese string: The background service port number is very important. After the foreground interface is started, it will obtain data from the background service.

中文字符串: 分站标识符，用于区分在同一计算机下部署的不同分站程序，允许填入一个及以上英文字母或阿拉伯数字，且以英文字母开始。
Chinese string: The substation identifier is used to distinguish different substation programs deployed on the same computer. One or more English letters or Arabic numerals are allowed and must start with an English letter.

中文字符串: 是否使用外部XRay控制器，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to use an external XRay controller, True if yes, False if no.

中文字符串:
外部X射线放射源控制器通讯参数，支持通过串口或者网口进行通讯。
    串口参数格式：Serial, Com端口名称, 波特率, 奇偶性（None/Odd/Even）, 数据位, 停止位(0/1/2/1.5)，例如：Serial, Com2, 115200, None, 8, 1
    网口参数格式：Tcp, IP地址:端口号，例如：Tcp, 192.168.0.7:8081
Chinese string: External X-ray source controller communication parameters, support communication through serial port or network port. Serial port parameter format: Serial, Com port name, baud rate, parity (None/Odd/Even), data bit, stop bit (0/1/2/1.5), for example: Serial, Com2, 115200, None, 8, 1 Network port parameter format: TCP, IP address: port number, for example: TCP, 192.168.0.7:8081

中文字符串: 外部XRay控制器目标管电压，单位：V，浮点数。
Chinese string: External XRay controller target tube voltage, unit: V, floating point number.

中文字符串: 外部XRay控制器目标管电流，单位：uA，浮点数。
Chinese string: External XRay controller target tube current, unit: uA, floating point number.

中文字符串: 是否允许输出外部XRay控制器调试信息，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to allow the output of external XRay controller debugging information, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 激光信号值偏移数量，整数。
Chinese string: Laser signal value offset amount, integer.

中文字符串: 激光原始分辨率大小，单位：毫米。
Chinese string: Laser native resolution size, unit: mm.

中文字符串: 激光光斑半径大小，单位：毫米，浮点数。
Chinese string: Laser spot radius, unit: mm, floating point number.

中文字符串: 激光原始数据分区大小，单位：毫米，浮点数。
Chinese string: Laser raw data partition size, unit: mm, floating point number.

中文字符串: 激光削薄区数据分区大小，单位：毫米，浮点数。
Chinese string: The size of the laser thinning area data partition, unit: mm, floating point number.

中文字符串: 激光图表控件分区大小（单位：毫米），留空时 代表使用文件分区大小作为图表控件分区大小。
Chinese string: Laser chart control partition size (unit: mm). If left blank, it means using the file partition size as the chart control partition size.

中文字符串: 激光图表控件削薄区分区大小（单位：毫米），留空时 代表使用削薄区文件分区大小作为削薄区图表控件分区大小。
Chinese string: The size of the thinning area partition of the laser chart control (unit: mm). If left blank, it means using the thinning area file partition size as the thinning area chart control partition size.

中文字符串: 激光基材边缘过滤半径，单位：毫米
Chinese string: Laser substrate edge filter radius, unit: mm

中文字符串: 激光设备特征参数，用于位置纠偏
Chinese string: Laser equipment characteristic parameters for position correction

中文字符串: 激光高斯滤波-窗口大小（整数值）
是否允许开启激光定向滤波功能，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to enable the laser directional filtering function, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 激光定向高斯滤波脚本
激光定向高斯滤波从边界点开始跳过的宽度，单位：毫米，浮点数。
Chinese string: The width that the laser directional Gaussian filter skips from the boundary point, unit: mm, floating point number.

中文字符串: 激光数据横向偏移，当此值为正时，正向趟向右偏，负向趟向左偏移，单位：毫米。
Chinese string: The laser data is offset horizontally. When this value is positive, the positive direction deviates to the right, and the negative direction deviates to the left. The unit is millimeter.

中文字符串: 激光是否允许小波去噪，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether the laser allows wavelet denoising, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 处理宽度，一般代指激光真实光斑大小，单位：毫米。
Chinese string: Processing width generally refers to the actual laser spot size, unit: millimeter.

中文字符串: 激光通道自动校正寻峰参数算法支持探测的最小峰值大小，浮点数。
Chinese string: The laser channel automatic correction peak search parameter algorithm supports the minimum peak size detected, floating point number.

中文字符串: 激光通道基材寻峰下限，浮点数。
Chinese string: The lower limit of the laser channel substrate peak search, a floating point number.

中文字符串: 激光通道涂层寻峰下限，浮点数。
Chinese string: Laser channel coating peak search lower limit, floating point number.

中文字符串: 激光通道单双面边交界处寻峰下限，浮点数。
Chinese string: The lower limit of the peak search at the junction of the single-sided and double-sided edges of the laser channel, a floating point number.

中文字符串: 激光峰宽限制，当峰宽小于此值时，不认为是一个独立的峰，单位：毫米，浮点数。
Chinese string: Laser peak width limit. When the peak width is smaller than this value, it is not considered as an independent peak. Unit: millimeter, floating point number.

中文字符串:
激光边界检测模式：
    Normal, 正常模式（使用探测器信号值检测，可检测出极片边）
    FixedColorTagger, 固定色标模式（使用单一色标固定在来料侧托辊上进行过滤，并配合信号值检测基材边方式，无法检测出极片边，仅支持单道间歇涂布）
    Valley, 波谷定制模式（使用探测器信号值检测，取极片上凹陷形态的数据，而不是突出形态的数据）
    FixedValuesBySubstrate, 相对于基材的固定值列表（使用配方中用户设定的留白/膜区宽度列表确定边界位置，起始位置相对于基材，仅支持连续涂布）
    AdvancedFixedValuesBySubstrate, 相对于基材的高级固定值列表（使用配方中用户设定的留白/膜区宽度列表初步确定边界位置，并在这些位置的附近使用探测器信号值查找更准确的位置，起始位置相对于基材，仅支持连续涂布）
    MovingColorTagger, 移动色标模式（使用与探测器固定在一起的移动色标来进行寻边，不支持单双面边检测）
    OnlySubstrate, 仅基材模式（使用探测器信号值检测最外侧边【使用基材寻峰参数】，将检测到的边视为基材涂层混合边）
    AutoMode, 自动模式（对于连续涂布和不走带时，认为没有头尾，基于基材宽度、涂层宽度自动判别各个峰值点及对应的特性来确定边界点性质，否则，认为有头尾，如果固定色标存在，走固定色标模式，否则，认为是连续涂布直接全部保留。）
Chinese string: Laser boundary detection mode: Normal, normal mode (using the detector signal value detection, the edge of the pole piece can be detected) FixedColorTagger, fixed color tag mode (using a single color tag fixed on the incoming side roller for filtering, and cooperating with the signal value to detect the substrate edge. The pole piece edge cannot be detected, and only single-pass intermittent coating is supported) Valley, valley customization mode (using the detector signal value detection, taking the data of the concave shape on the pole piece instead of the protruding shape) FixedValuesBySubstrate, a fixed value list relative to the substrate (using the blank/film area width list set by the user in the recipe to determine the boundary position, the starting position is relative to the substrate, and only continuous coating is supported) AdvancedFixedValuesBySubstrate, an advanced fixed value list relative to the substrate (using the blank/film area width list set by the user in the recipe to preliminarily determine the boundary position, and use the detector signal value near these positions to find a more accurate position, the starting position is relative to the substrate, and only continuous coating is supported) MovingColorTagger, moving color tag mode (using the moving color tag fixed to the detector to find the edge, single-sided and double-sided edge detection is not supported) OnlySubstrate, Substrate-only mode (use the detector signal value to detect the outermost edge [use the substrate peak search parameter], and regard the detected edge as a substrate-coating mixed edge) AutoMode, automatic mode (for continuous coating and no tape running, it is considered that there is no head or tail, and each peak point and the corresponding characteristics are automatically determined based on the substrate width and coating width to determine the nature of the boundary point. Otherwise, it is considered to have a head or tail. If a fixed color mark exists, the fixed color mark mode is used. Otherwise, it is considered to be continuous coating and all are retained directly.)

中文字符串: 是否允许激光通道开启寻边智能纠偏算法，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to allow the laser channel to start the edge-finding intelligent correction algorithm, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 激光通道寻边智能纠偏算法相似度比较半径，单位：毫米，浮点数。
Chinese string: Similarity comparison radius of the laser channel edge-finding intelligent deviation correction algorithm, unit: mm, floating point number.

中文字符串: 在高级固定值列表寻边方案下，自动找更准确的位置时的搜索半径大小，同时也是激光分离信号分别寻边时的搜索范围，单位：毫米，浮点数。
Chinese string: In the advanced fixed value list edge search scheme, the search radius size for automatically finding a more accurate position is also the search range when the laser separation signal is separately searching for edges. Unit: mm, floating point number.

中文字符串: 激光中位数滤波宽度，单位：毫米，浮点数。
Chinese string: Laser median filter width, unit: mm, floating point number.

中文字符串: 激光均值滤波宽度，单位：毫米，浮点数。
Chinese string: Laser mean filter width, unit: mm, floating point number.

中文字符串: 是否移除激光通道无意义点，是：True，否：False
Chinese string: Whether to remove meaningless points in the laser channel, yes: True, no: False

中文字符串: 激光通道无意义点下界值（低于该值视为无意义）
Chinese string: The lower limit of the meaningless point of the laser channel (below this value is considered meaningless)
Laser channel coefficient K, floating point number.
Laser channel coefficient B, floating point number.
Laser channel 2 coefficient K, floating point number.
Laser channel 2 coefficient B, floating point number.
Laser channel 3 coefficient K, floating point number.
Laser channel 3 coefficient B, floating point number.
Laser channel 4 coefficient K, floating point number.
Laser channel 4 coefficient B, floating point number.

中文字符串: 在激光设备存在时，是否启用激光信号跟踪功能，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to enable the laser signal tracking function when a laser device exists, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 激光第一跟踪起始位置，单位：毫米，浮点数。
Chinese string: The starting position of the first laser tracking, unit: mm, floating point number.

中文字符串: 激光第一跟踪结束位置，单位：毫米，浮点数。
Chinese string: The end position of the first laser tracking, unit: mm, floating point number.

中文字符串: 激光第二跟踪起始位置，单位：毫米，浮点数。
Chinese string: The starting position of the second laser tracking, unit: mm, floating point number.

中文字符串: 激光第二跟踪结束位置，单位：毫米，浮点数。
Chinese string: The second laser tracking end position, unit: mm, floating point number.

中文字符串: 激光警报允许标准片测量到的最大变化率，超过此变化率，软件将报激光异常，浮点数。
Chinese string: The laser alarm allows the standard film to measure the maximum rate of change. If this rate of change is exceeded, the software will report a laser abnormality and a floating point number.

中文字符串: 重置激光器的目标信号值。
Chinese string: Reset the target signal value of the laser.

中文字符串: 重置激光器错容比率，默认值千分之一。
Chinese string: Reset the laser fault tolerance ratio, the default value is one thousandth.

中文字符串: 激光重置最大重试次数，正整数。
Chinese string: The maximum number of laser reset retries, a positive integer.

中文字符串: 固定激光模式下寻峰下限值。
Chinese string: Fixed the lower limit of peak search in laser mode.

中文字符串: 固定激光模式下寻峰宽度限值，单位：毫米。
Chinese string: Peak search width limit in fixed laser mode, unit: mm.

中文字符串: 固定激光模式报表分区大小，单位：毫米，浮点数。
Chinese string: Fixed laser mode report partition size, unit: mm, floating point number.

中文字符串: 固定激光模式涂布方向单片最大长度，单位：毫米，浮点数。
Chinese string: The maximum length of a single piece in the coating direction of a fixed laser mode, unit: mm, floating point number.

中文字符串: 固定激光模式实时扫描图分区大小，单位：毫米，浮点数。
Chinese string: Fixed laser mode real-time scan image partition size, unit: mm, floating point number.

中文字符串: 激光跟踪采集趟数（采集够N趟的数据就更新一次跟踪值），N为正整数。
Chinese string: The number of laser tracking collection passes (the tracking value is updated once N passes of data are collected), where N is a positive integer.

中文字符串: 是否开启激光带通滤波，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to enable laser bandpass filtering, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 以有效频率为分母，目标频率为分子的激光带阻范围小数表示，范围为(0-1]，样例：0.2-0.3;0.44-0.48
Chinese string: The laser band stop range is expressed as a decimal with the effective frequency as the denominator and the target frequency as the numerator. The range is (0-1], example: 0.2-0.3; 0.44-0.48

中文字符串: 激光趟数据带通滤波系数，值越小带阻越大，浮点数，范围为[0-1]。
Chinese string: The bandpass filter coefficient of laser data. The smaller the value, the larger the band stop. It is a floating point number in the range of [0-1].

中文字符串: 激光原始报表带通滤波系数，值越小带阻越大，浮点数，范围为[0-1]。
Chinese string: Laser raw report bandpass filter coefficient. The smaller the value, the larger the band stop. It is a floating point number in the range of [0-1].

中文字符串: 激光标定采样周数，单位：Cycle，正整数。
Chinese string: Laser calibration sampling cycles, unit: Cycle, positive integer.

中文字符串:
激光标准片第一组采样位置及对应厚度列表，格式为：标准片1起始位置-标准片1结束位置,标准片1厚度;标准片2起始位置-标准片2结束位置,标准片2厚度;...
    样例：24-103,160.2;150-180,170.3
    固定使用第二个标准片的厚度作为激光跟踪初始值
    固定使用第三个标准片作为标准片警报依据
Chinese string: The first set of sampling positions and corresponding thickness list of laser standard films, the format is: Standard film 1 starting position - standard film 1 end position, standard film 1 thickness; Standard film 2 starting position - standard film 2 end position, standard film 2 thickness;... Example: 24-103,160.2;150-180,170.3 The thickness of the second standard film is fixedly used as the initial value of laser tracking. The third standard film is fixedly used as the basis for standard film alarm.

中文字符串:
激光标注片第二组采样位置及对应厚度列表，格式为：标准片1起始位置-标准片1结束位置,标准片1厚度;标准片2起始位置-标准片2结束位置,标准片2厚度;...
    样例：24-103,160.2;150-180,170.3
Chinese string: The second set of sampling positions and corresponding thickness list of laser-marked sheets, the format is: Standard sheet 1 starting position - Standard sheet 1 end position, Standard sheet 1 thickness; Standard sheet 2 starting position - Standard sheet 2 end position, Standard sheet 2 thickness;... Example: 24-103,160.2; 150-180,170.3

中文字符串: 激光标准片是否是可移动的，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether the laser standard is removable, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 激光可移动标准片宽度，单位：毫米，浮点数。
Chinese string: Width of the laser movable standard sheet, unit: mm, floating point number.

中文字符串: 激光可移动标准片宽度容差半径，单位：毫米，浮点数。
Chinese string: The width tolerance radius of the laser movable standard piece, unit: mm, floating point number.

中文字符串: 激光可移动标准片取样宽度，取样的中心为检测到的标准片位置中心，单位：毫米，浮点数。
Chinese string: The sampling width of the laser movable standard piece. The sampling center is the detected center of the standard piece position. Unit: mm, floating point number.

中文字符串: 激光传感器1与激光传感器2之间的相对距离，单位：毫米，浮点数。
Chinese string: The relative distance between laser sensor 1 and laser sensor 2, unit: mm, floating point number.

中文字符串: 重置激光器位置1，单位：毫米，浮点数。
Chinese string: Reset laser position 1, unit: mm, floating point number.

中文字符串: 重置激光器位置2，单位：毫米，浮点数。
Chinese string: Reset laser position 2, unit: mm, floating point number.

中文字符串: 激光通道超限（非法）信号绝对值，激光通道信号的绝对值大于此值时，信号将被强制设置为0，浮点数，该值大于0时，起作用。
Chinese string: The absolute value of the laser channel over-limit (illegal) signal. When the absolute value of the laser channel signal is greater than this value, the signal will be forced to be set to 0. It is a floating point number. When the value is greater than 0, it takes effect.

中文字符串: 激光第一标准片起始位置，单位：毫米，浮点数。
Chinese string: The starting position of the first laser standard film, unit: mm, floating point number.

中文字符串: 激光第一标准片结束位置，单位：毫米，浮点数。
Chinese string: The end position of the first laser standard film, unit: mm, floating point number.

中文字符串: 激光第二标准片起始位置，单位：毫米，浮点数。
Chinese string: The starting position of the second laser standard film, unit: mm, floating point number.

中文字符串: 激光第二标准片结束位置，单位：毫米，浮点数。
Chinese string: End position of the second laser standard film, unit: mm, floating point number.

中文字符串: 双激光头设备双头数据融合时的人工辅助信号偏移量，浮点数。
Chinese string: The artificial auxiliary signal offset during dual-head data fusion of dual-head laser head equipment, floating point number.

中文字符串: 是否允许通过标准片自动调整两激光头融合时的偏移量，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to allow automatic adjustment of the offset between the two laser heads when they are fused through the standard film, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 双激光头设备双头数据下探头融合时的人工辅助信号偏移量，浮点数。
Chinese string: The artificial auxiliary signal offset when the probes are fused under dual-head data of dual-laser head equipment, floating point number.

中文字符串: 激光信号分离（A、B分别输出）模式下A头相对于B头的错位长度，即B头数据位置加上多少offset后，可以与A头对齐，单位：毫米，浮点数。
Chinese string: The offset length of head A relative to head B in laser signal separation (A and B are output separately) mode, that is, the offset added to the data position of head B to align with head A, unit: mm, floating point number.

中文字符串: 是否开启激光分离信号无效值过滤功能，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to enable the laser separation signal invalid value filtering function, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 激光分离信号1的无效数据对应的值，浮点数。
Chinese string: The value corresponding to the invalid data of laser separation signal 1, a floating point number.

中文字符串: 激光分离信号2的无效数据对应的值，浮点数。
Chinese string: The value corresponding to the invalid data of laser separation signal 2, a floating point number.

中文字符串: 激光分离信号无效值的半径，在这个半径范围内视为无效，浮点数。
Chinese string: The radius of invalid values of laser separation signal. It is considered invalid within this radius. It is a floating point number.

中文字符串: 激光在提取膜区平均信号时，用于过滤非法信号所用的标准差计算阈值（小于此值对应的数据有效）。
Chinese string: When the laser extracts the average signal of the membrane area, it is used to filter out the standard deviation calculation threshold used for illegal signals (data smaller than this value are valid).

中文字符串: 激光在判定削薄区结束位置时，与单面膜区均值的差值，浮点数。
Chinese string: When the laser determines the end position of the thinning area, it is the difference between the average value of the single-sided film area, a floating point number.

中文字符串: 激光在判定削薄区结束位置时，与双面膜区均值的差值，浮点数。
Chinese string: When the laser determines the end position of the thinning area, it is the difference between the average value of the double-sided film area, a floating point number.

中文字符串: 激光削薄区最大可能宽度。单位：毫米，浮点数。
Chinese string: Maximum possible width of the laser thinned area. Unit: mm, floating point number.

中文字符串: 激光削薄区信号连续多少毫米都小于削薄区结束百分比所表示的厚度时认为已经稳定，单位：毫米，浮点数。
Chinese string: The laser thinning zone signal is considered stable when the thickness represented by the thinning zone end percentage is continuously less than the thickness of the thinning zone for a certain number of millimeters. Unit: millimeter, floating point number.

中文字符串: 单激光头寻边搜索半径，单位：毫米，浮点数。
Chinese string: Edge search radius of a single laser head, unit: mm, floating point number.

中文字符串: 单激光头寻边处理宽度，单位：毫米，浮点数。
Chinese string: Single laser head edge processing width, unit: mm, floating point number.

中文字符串: 单激光头A寻边寻峰下限，浮点数。
Chinese string: Lower limit of edge and peak search for single laser head A, floating point number.

中文字符串: 单激光头B寻边寻峰下限，浮点数。
Chinese string: Lower limit of edge and peak search for single laser head B, floating point number.

中文字符串: 单激光头A寻边峰宽下限，单位：毫米，浮点数。
Chinese string: Lower limit of edge-seeking peak width of single laser head A, unit: mm, floating point number.

中文字符串: 单激光头B寻边峰宽下限，单位：毫米，浮点数。
Chinese string: Lower limit of edge-seeking peak width of single laser head B, unit: mm, floating point number.

中文字符串: 是否使用激光动态标准片位置，改方案仅支持普通激光设备，不支持双激光头设备！是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to use the laser dynamic standard film position. This solution only supports ordinary laser equipment, not dual laser head equipment! Yes: True, No: False.

中文字符串: 激光动态标准片起始位置（相对于近原点基材边），单位：毫米，浮点数。
Chinese string: The starting position of the laser dynamic standard film (relative to the substrate edge near the origin), unit: mm, floating point number.

中文字符串: 激光动态标准片结束位置（相对于近原点基材边），单位：毫米，浮点数。
Chinese string: The end position of the laser dynamic standard film (relative to the substrate edge near the origin), unit: mm, floating point number.

中文字符串: 测零时是否允许重置激光，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to allow laser resetting when measuring zero, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 是否开启激光差值滤波，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to enable laser difference filtering, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 激光差值滤波次数，正整数。
Chinese string: Laser difference filtering times, a positive integer.

中文字符串: 激光是否过滤无效数据，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether the laser filters invalid data, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 无效数据过滤取样宽度，单位：毫米，浮点数。
Chinese string: Invalid data filtering sampling width, unit: mm, floating point number.

中文字符串: 激光跟踪与警报只参考负向数据，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Laser tracking and alarm only refer to negative data, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 激光膜区补偿值，数组，英文逗号隔开。
Chinese string: Laser film area compensation value, array, separated by commas.

中文字符串: 激光分区补偿值,以‘;’隔开膜区，以‘,’隔开分区，如：‘0,1;3’代表第一膜区第二分区补偿1，第二膜区第一分区补偿3。
Chinese string: Laser partition compensation value, with ';' separating film areas and ',' separating partitions, such as '0,1;3' means compensation 1 for the second partition of the first film area and compensation 3 for the first partition of the second film area.

中文字符串: 激光通道是否使用涂层边进行校验而不是基材边进行校验，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether the laser channel uses the coating side for calibration instead of the substrate side, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 激光单面校验允许修正的最大B值修正量，浮点数。
Chinese string: The maximum B value correction allowed for single-sided laser calibration, a floating point number.

中文字符串: 激光双面校验允许修正的最大B值修正量，浮点数。
Chinese string: The maximum B value correction allowed for laser double-sided calibration, a floating point number.

中文字符串: 是否允许开启激光横向N点平滑算法进行滤波，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to enable the laser lateral N-point smoothing algorithm for filtering, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 参与一次激光平滑运算的数据点的一阶差分序列的上限，即要求参与平滑运算的相邻两个数据值不能差异太大，如果大于等于此上限则放弃此次滤波运算，保持数据原始值。此参数仅应用于横向N点平滑。
Chinese string: The upper limit of the first-order difference sequence of the data points participating in a laser smoothing operation, that is, the difference between the two adjacent data values participating in the smoothing operation cannot be too large. If it is greater than or equal to this upper limit, the filtering operation is abandoned and the original data value is maintained. This parameter is only applied to horizontal N-point smoothing.

中文字符串: 横向平滑系数数组，定义每个点由多少个点计算而来及权重系数，浮点数。
Chinese string: Array of horizontal smoothing coefficients, defining how many points each point is calculated from and the weight coefficient, floating point number.

中文字符串: 是否允许使用激光横向滤波算法2（膜区均值+系数），是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to allow the use of laser lateral filtering algorithm 2 (membrane area mean + coefficient), yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 激光横向滤波算法2（膜区均值+系数）系数，浮点数，(0,1]
Chinese string: Laser lateral filtering algorithm 2 (membrane area mean + coefficient) coefficient, floating point number, (0,1]

中文字符串: 是否允许激光使用横向滤波算法3（膜区多项式趋势+系数），是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to allow the laser to use lateral filtering algorithm 3 (membrane area polynomial trend + coefficient), yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 激光横向滤波算法3（膜区多项式趋势+系数）多项式次方数，正整数
Chinese string: Laser lateral filtering algorithm 3 (film area polynomial trend + coefficient) polynomial power, positive integer

中文字符串: 激光横向滤波算法3（膜区多项式趋势+系数）系数，原值占比，浮点数，[0,1]
Chinese string: Laser lateral filtering algorithm 3 (film area polynomial trend + coefficient) coefficient, original value ratio, floating point number, [0,1]

中文字符串: 是否允许开启纵向N点平滑算法进行滤波，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to enable the vertical N-point smoothing algorithm for filtering, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 纵向N点平滑的权值数组，每个<double>代表一趟数据对应位置的权值，第一个元素代表离当前趟最远的一趟的权值。有几个元素就有几趟的数据参与运算（包含当前趟）。
Chinese string: The weight array of N-point vertical smoothing, each <double> represents the weight of a trip corresponding to the position, the first element represents the weight of the trip farthest from the current trip. There are as many elements as there are trips of data involved in the calculation (including the current trip).

中文字符串: 参与一次激光平滑运算的数据点的极差的上限，即要求参与平滑运算的数据值不能波动太大，如果大于等于此上限则放弃此次滤波运算，保持数据原始值。此参数同时应用于纵向N点平滑和纵向单值滤波。
Chinese string: The upper limit of the range of the data points involved in a laser smoothing operation, that is, the data value involved in the smoothing operation should not fluctuate too much. If it is greater than or equal to this upper limit, the filtering operation is abandoned and the original data value is maintained. This parameter is applied to both longitudinal N-point smoothing and longitudinal single-value filtering.

中文字符串: 在当涂布时，是否允许开启激光纵向N点平滑算法进行滤波，是：True，否：False。注意，仅在开启纵向平滑时该参数才有效，不区分是否削薄区数据。
Chinese string: When coating, whether to enable the laser longitudinal N-point smoothing algorithm for filtering, yes: True, no: False. Note that this parameter is only valid when longitudinal smoothing is enabled, regardless of whether the thinning area data is used.

中文字符串: 是否允许开启提取削薄区用纵向N点平滑算法进行滤波，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to enable the extraction of thinning areas and filter them using the longitudinal N-point smoothing algorithm, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 提取激光削薄区用纵向N点平滑的权值数组，每个<double>代表一趟数据对应位置的权值，第一个元素代表离当前趟最远的一趟的权值。有几个元素就有几趟的数据参与运算（包含当前趟）。
Chinese string: Extract the weight array of N-point longitudinal smoothing of the laser thinning area. Each <double> represents the weight of a data position. The first element represents the weight of the farthest data from the current data. The number of elements is the number of data involved in the calculation (including the current data).

中文字符串: 激光削薄区参与一次平滑运算的数据点的极差的上限，即要求参与平滑运算的数据值不能波动太大，如果大于等于此上限则放弃此次滤波运算，保持数据原始值。此参数同时应用于纵向N点平滑和纵向单值滤波。
Chinese string: The upper limit of the range of the data points participating in the smoothing operation in the laser thinning area, that is, the data value participating in the smoothing operation should not fluctuate too much. If it is greater than or equal to this upper limit, the filtering operation is abandoned and the original data value is maintained. This parameter is applied to both longitudinal N-point smoothing and longitudinal single-value filtering.

中文字符串: 是否允许激光使用纵向单值滤波算法，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to allow the laser to use the longitudinal single value filtering algorithm, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 激光纵向单值滤波算法系数，该系数应用于单值，浮点数，[0,1)
Chinese string: Laser longitudinal single-value filtering algorithm coefficient, this coefficient is applied to single value, floating point number, [0,1)

中文字符串: 是否允许激光削薄区使用纵向单值滤波算法，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to allow the laser thinning area to use the longitudinal single-value filtering algorithm, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 激光削薄区纵向单值滤波算法系数，该系数应用于单值，浮点数，[0,1)
Chinese string: The coefficient of the laser thinning area longitudinal single-value filtering algorithm. This coefficient is applied to single values, floating point numbers, [0,1)

中文字符串: 是否开启手动无效分区筛选，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to enable manual invalid partition filtering, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 无效分区筛选配置。激光分区占比系数列表,以‘;’隔开膜区，以‘,’隔开分区，如：‘1,0.3;0.2’代表第一膜区第二分区为无效分区，无效分区信号占比为0.3，第二膜区第一分区为无效分区，无效分区信号占比为0.2。
Chinese string: Invalid partition screening configuration. Laser partition ratio coefficient list, with ';' to separate the film area, and ',' to separate the partition, such as: '1,0.3;0.2' means that the second partition of the first film area is an invalid partition, and the invalid partition signal ratio is 0.3, and the first partition of the second film area is an invalid partition, and the invalid partition signal ratio is 0.2.

中文字符串: 进行无效分区筛选时，是否总是使用无效分区计算趟均值（不区分手动/自动），是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: When performing invalid partition screening, whether to always use the invalid partition to calculate the mean (regardless of manual/automatic), yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 是否允许开启趟数据优化功能，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to enable the data optimization function, yes: True, no: False.
The lower limit of K value, floating point number.

中文字符串: 横向分区稳定系数，浮点数。
Chinese string: Horizontal partition stability coefficient, floating point number.

中文字符串: 横向分区优化弱化系数，浮点数。
Chinese string: Horizontal partition optimization weakening coefficient, floating point number.

中文字符串: 是否允许开启激光标准片修正1，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to allow the laser standard film correction 1 to be enabled, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 激光标准片修正1靠近值半径差值，浮点数，如设置为2时，[98-102]范围内的数就都被判定为靠近100的值。
Chinese string: Laser standard film correction 1 close to the value radius difference, floating point number, if it is set to 2, the numbers in the range of [98-102] will be judged as values close to 100.

中文字符串: 激光标准片修正1真实值占比，浮点数，[0,1]，值越大越接近测量真实值。
Chinese string: The percentage of the true value of the laser standard film correction 1, floating point number, [0,1]. The larger the value, the closer it is to the measured true value.

中文字符串: 已知激光标准片厚度列表库，各数值为浮点数，用“;”隔开，如：“34;124;33;22”。
Chinese string: list library of known laser standard sheet thicknesses. Each value is a floating point number separated by ";", such as: "34;124;33;22".

中文字符串: 开封测控 X 射线测厚仪
Chinese string: Kaifeng Measurement and Control X-ray Thickness Gauge

中文字符串: 开封测控 Beta 射线测厚仪
Chinese string: Kaifeng Measurement and Control Beta X-ray Thickness Gauge

中文字符串: 开封测控 激光 测厚仪
Chinese string: Kaifeng measurement and control laser thickness gauge

中文字符串: 开封测控 一体机 测厚仪
Chinese string: Kaifeng measurement and control integrated machine thickness gauge

中文字符串: 正在整理并保存数据文件...
正在整理并保存数据中，请耐心等待，切勿强制关闭软件...
Chinese string: The data is being sorted and saved. Please wait patiently and do not force close the software...

中文字符串: 正在寻边中，完成后将自动开始采样，请稍候...
Chinese string: Finding the edge, sampling will start automatically after completion, please wait...

中文字符串: 成功：{success}，位移：{hasMoved}，左侧基材：{leftY}，右侧基材：{rightY}。
Chinese string: Success: {success}, displacement: {hasMoved}, left substrate: {leftY}, right substrate: {rightY}.

中文字符串: 修正了一处Y坐标，坐标位置为{startY}-{endY}
Chinese string: Corrected a Y coordinate, the coordinate position is {startY}-{endY}

中文字符串: 软件无法从最近一次保存的配置文件中读取配置信息，我们已通过自动保存的配置文件备份加载配置，可能存在某些最近的配置改动丢失的问题！\r请知悉，我们深表歉意！\r请现场服务人员将此问题告知开发人员，谢谢！
Chinese string: The software cannot read the configuration information from the most recently saved configuration file. We have loaded the configuration from the automatically saved configuration file backup. Some recent configuration changes may be lost! \rPlease be aware and we apologize! \rPlease ask the field service personnel to inform the developer of this problem, thank you!

中文字符串: 解析被阻止的图表ModuleId失败。
Chinese string: Failed to resolve blocked chart ModuleId.

中文字符串: 程序后台正在写入数据，强行退出将造成数据丢失，请稍后再次尝试退出程序！
Chinese string: The program is writing data in the background. Forced exit will cause data loss. Please try to exit the program again later!
Are you sure you want to exit the application?

中文字符串: 各架 {parameterName} 不一致，请先统一设置 {parameterName} 参数后再尝试开启同步扫描！
Chinese string: The {parameterName} of each frame is inconsistent. Please set the {parameterName} parameters uniformly before trying to start synchronous scanning!

中文字符串: {EnvironmentVariables.SubstationContexts[i].DisplayName} 发生器尚未就绪，无法开启自动启停！
Chinese string: {EnvironmentVariables.SubstationContexts[i].DisplayName} The generator is not ready yet, automatic start and stop cannot be enabled!

中文字符串: 各架 {parameterName} 参数不一致，请先统一设置 {parameterName} 参数后再尝试开启自动启停！
Chinese string: The {parameterName} parameters of each frame are inconsistent. Please set the {parameterName} parameters uniformly before trying to enable automatic start and stop!

中文字符串: 已连接到分站，无需重连！
Chinese string: Already connected to the outstation, no need to reconnect!

中文字符串: 请为当前布局设置一个名称。
Chinese string: Please set a name for the current layout.

中文字符串: 已存在以当前名称命名的布局，请换个名称再试。
Chinese string: A layout with the current name already exists. Please try again with a different name.

中文字符串: 未选择配方，将无法产生测量数据，是否继续？
Chinese string: Without selecting a recipe, measurement data cannot be generated. Do you want to continue?

中文字符串: 未选择配方，用户选择新建卷。
Chinese string: No recipe was selected and the user selected Create New Volume.

中文字符串: 卷号没有更新，仍然要开启一个新卷吗？
Chinese string: The volume number has not been updated. Do you still want to open a new volume?
A new volume has been opened!

中文字符串: 卷号没有更新，仍然要开启一个新卷吗？
Chinese string: The volume number has not been updated. Do you still want to open a new volume?
A new volume has been opened!

中文字符串: 确定要开启一个新的临时卷吗？
Chinese string: Are you sure you want to open a new temporary volume?
A new volume has been opened!

中文字符串: 正在涂布，不允许重置X方向坐标！
Chinese string: Coating in progress, resetting the X-direction coordinate is not allowed!

中文字符串: 确定要重启本应用程序吗？
Chinese string: Are you sure you want to restart this application?

中文字符串: 多架模式联动自动启停
Chinese string: Multi-frame mode linkage automatic start and stop

中文字符串: 导出所有配置元数据及当前值
Chinese string: Export all configuration metadata and current values

中文字符串: 保存失败，请检查文件是否被占用！
Chinese string: Failed to save, please check if the file is occupied!

中文字符串: 自动启停已开启，无法完成 {actionName} 操作！
Chinese string: Automatic start/stop is enabled, unable to complete {actionName} operation!

中文字符串: 为工具对话框准备环境失败。
Chinese string: Failed to prepare environment for tool dialog box.

中文字符串: 工具对话框初始化失败。
为工具对话框准备环境失败。
Chinese string: Failed to prepare environment for tool dialog box.

中文字符串: 工具对话框初始化失败。

Chinese string: After the data is written in the background, it is completed.
The configuration file has been saved.

中文字符串: 立刻保存配置文件和零位数据
Chinese string: Immediately save configuration files and zero position data

中文字符串: 多架模式联动自动启停
Chinese string: Multi-frame mode linkage automatic start and stop

中文字符串: 开封测控测厚仪管理工作站
Chinese string: Kaifeng measurement and control thickness gauge management workstation

中文字符串: 统一管理用户所有配方。
统一管理用户所有工艺参数及配方。
Chinese string: Centrally manage all user process parameters and recipes.
Adjust the upper computer software parameters.

中文字符串: 测量各个传感器之间的长度。
Chinese string: Measure the length between each sensor.

中文字符串: 主界面右侧概览区域，辅助用户掌握设备当前状态。
Chinese string: The overview area on the right side of the main interface helps users understand the current status of the device.
Displays the status of the substation.

中文字符串: 提供调试多架设备的操作功能，是硬件工程师维护与修理测厚仪的必备工具。
Chinese string: It provides the function of debugging multiple devices and is an essential tool for hardware engineers to maintain and repair thickness gauges.
Display the status of each substation.

中文字符串: 专用于查看设备异常信息。
Chinese string: Dedicated to viewing device abnormality information.

中文字符串: 查看软件输出的日志文件信息。
Chinese string: View the log file information output by the software.

中文字符串: 通过本界面管理主站和分站高级权限。
Chinese string: Use this interface to manage the advanced permissions of the main site and sub-sites.

中文字符串: 用于提示用户录入膜卷信息。
Chinese string: Used to prompt the user to enter film roll information.

中文字符串: 涂布方向趟最大额外缓存米数，单位：米，浮点数。
Chinese string: The maximum number of additional buffer meters in the coating direction, unit: meter, floating point number.

中文字符串: 缓存的最新一趟与提取目标位置之间允许的最大距离，单位：米，浮点数。该参数是为了解决当两架距离过近时，提取目标可能位于最新缓存趟的后方，从而导致提取失败的问题。
Chinese string: The maximum distance allowed between the latest cached trip and the extraction target location, in meters, floating point number. This parameter is to solve the problem that when the distance between the two aircraft is too close, the extraction target may be behind the latest cached trip, resulting in extraction failure.

中文字符串: 自定义配方涂布类型后缀符，格式为“X;X;X”，英文分号隔开，分别对应基材、单面、双面配方的后缀符号。可留空或部分留空以使用应用默认值。
Chinese string: Custom formula coating type suffix, the format is "X;X;X", separated by English semicolons, corresponding to the suffix symbols of substrate, single-sided, and double-sided formulas respectively. It can be left blank or partially left blank to use the application default value.

中文字符串: 同步初始化完成时是否清理数据匹配用缓存，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to clear the data matching cache when synchronization initialization is completed, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 图表显示范围（公差的倍数。例如，2代表图表显示范围为公差范围的两倍）
Chinese string: Chart display range (multiple of tolerance. For example, 2 means the chart display range is twice the tolerance range)

中文字符串: 每隔多少小时，自动保存一次配置（单位：小时，浮点数）。
Chinese string: How often to save the configuration automatically (unit: hours, floating point number)

中文字符串: 自动启停-启动前等待时间下限值（单位：秒）
Chinese string: Automatic start-stop-lower limit of waiting time before starting (unit: seconds)

中文字符串: 自动启停-停止前等待时间下限值（单位：秒）
Chinese string: Automatic start-stop-lower limit of waiting time before stopping (unit: seconds)

中文字符串: 自动启停开启时启动/复位扫描是否给予提示，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to give a prompt when starting/resetting the scan when automatic start/stop is turned on, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 修改工程师模式参数时，是否需要强制要求设备未启动扫描，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: When modifying engineer mode parameters, whether it is necessary to force the device to not start scanning, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 自动生成卷功能开启时，最少允许用户设置单卷最多趟数，整数。
Chinese string: When the automatic roll generation function is turned on, the user is allowed to set the maximum number of passes for a single roll, which should be an integer.

中文字符串: 自动生成卷功能开启时，最多允许用户设置单卷最多趟数，整数。
Chinese string: When the automatic roll generation function is turned on, the user is allowed to set the maximum number of passes for a single roll, which is an integer.

中文字符串: 图表统计文字模板，留空使用软件内置模板，支持如下占位符： {mean} - 平均值, {weight} - 总重量, {max} - 最大值, {min} - 最小值, {sd} - 标准差, {cv} - 变异系数, {cv.net} - 净重变异系数, {range} - 全距/极差， 格式化标签： balabala 中的文字 balabala 将加粗显示。 balabala 中的文字 balabala 将斜体显示。 balabala 中的文字 balabala 将出现下划线。 balabala 中的文字 balabala 将出现删除线。
Chinese string: Chart statistics text template, leave it blank to use the software built-in template, supports the following placeholders: {mean} - mean, {weight} - total weight, {max} - maximum, {min} - minimum, {sd} - standard deviation, {cv} - coefficient of variation, {cv.net} - net weight coefficient of variation, {range} - range/extreme difference, Formatting tags: The text balabala in balabala will be bold. The text balabala in balabala will be italic. The text balabala in balabala will be underlined. The text balabala in balabala will be deleted.

中文字符串: 在多少分钟内重启自动恢复关闭软件时的卷信息（趟号），单位：分钟，浮点数。
Chinese string: The number of minutes it takes to restart and automatically restore the volume information (pass number) when the software was shut down. Unit: minute, floating point number.

中文字符串: 柱状图、面积图 是否从中心线位置开始显示，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether the bar chart and area chart are displayed from the center line position, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 是否去除设备厂商Logo，是：True，否：False
Chinese string: Whether to remove the device manufacturer's logo, yes: True, no: False

中文字符串: 是否一次性导出所有配方，是：True，否：False，仅导出当前选中的配方。
Chinese string: Whether to export all recipes at once, yes: True, no: False, only the currently selected recipe will be exported.

中文字符串: 纵向趋势图/CPK最多显示的趟数，单位：趟，自然数
Chinese string: Vertical trend chart/CPK maximum number of times displayed, unit: times, natural number

中文字符串: 纵向趋势图/CPK默认可视趟数，该值应当小于等于最多显示趟数，单位：趟，自然数
Chinese string: The default number of visible trips in the vertical trend chart/CPK should be less than or equal to the maximum number of trips displayed. Unit: trip, natural number

中文字符串: 纵向趋势图/CPK是否在尾部添加数据而不是头部，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether the vertical trend chart/CPK adds data at the end instead of the head, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 实时扫描图重命名名称，为空时使用默认名称，否则使用填入的名称。
Chinese string: Rename the real-time scan image. If it is empty, use the default name, otherwise use the filled name.

中文字符串: 断面扫描图（动态）重命名名称，为空时使用默认名称，否则使用填入的名称。
Chinese string: Rename the cross-sectional scan (dynamically). If it is empty, the default name will be used, otherwise the filled name will be used.

中文字符串: 异常信息面板最多显示的异常条数，正整数。
Chinese string: The maximum number of exceptions that can be displayed in the exception information panel, a positive integer.

中文字符串: 是否显示异常消息弹窗，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to display the exception message pop-up window, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 是否使用单独管理各分站的旧式配方管理模式，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to use the old recipe management mode of managing each substation separately, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 实时扫描图缓存输出点数，自然数。代表换数据点数每缓存多少个后才输出，缓存点数越大越“卡”，但性能损耗越少。
Chinese string: The number of points in the real-time scan image cache output, a natural number. It represents the number of data points that need to be cached before output. The larger the number of cache points, the more "stuck" it is, but the less performance loss it will have.

中文字符串: 实时数据列表是否使用渐变色默认值，将在未来版本中删除，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether the real-time data list uses the gradient color default value, which will be deleted in the future version. Yes: True, No: False.

中文字符串: 是否允许创建临时卷，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to allow the creation of temporary volumes, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 是否允许使用快捷键（Ctrl+Shift+Alt+K）激活隐藏的密码登录方式，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to allow the use of shortcut keys (Ctrl+Shift+Alt+K) to activate the hidden password login method, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 是否允许软件窗口状态从最小化变到最大化时自动还原一次界面布局，用于解决某些情况下图表未完全显示问题，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to allow the software window to automatically restore the interface layout once when the state changes from minimized to maximized, which is used to solve the problem of incomplete display of charts in some cases. Yes: True, No: False.

中文字符串:
测量物理量，用于定义配方管理中显示的参数名称，支持以下物理量：
    Weight, 重量
    Thickness, 厚度
Chinese string: Measure physical quantities, used to define parameter names displayed in recipe management, supporting the following physical quantities: Weight, Thickness,

中文字符串: 软件显示的测量值的单位，留空则不显示。
Chinese string: The unit of measurement value displayed by the software. If left blank, no display will occur.

中文字符串: 是否显示图表方向提示文字，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to display the chart direction prompt text, yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串:
图表方向左侧提示文字，格式：提示文字[;边框颜色]。 提示文字支持html标签自定义文字样式，支持以下语法： balabala 中的文字 balabala 将加粗显示。 balabala 中的文字 balabala 将斜体显示。 balabala 中的文字 balabala 将出现下划线。 balabala 中的文字 balabala 将出现删除线。
代表一个换行符 balabala 中的文字 balabala 将变为指定颜色 balabala 中的文字 balabala 背景色将变为指定颜色 边框颜色特别说明，设置为transparent将不显示边框。
Chinese string:
Hint text on the left side of the chart direction, format: Hint text [; border color]. Hint text supports HTML tag custom text style, and supports the following syntax: The text balabala in balabala will be displayed in bold. The text balabala in balabala will be displayed in italics. The text balabala in balabala will be underlined. The text balabala in balabala will be struck through.
represents a line break The text balabala in balabala will change to the specified color The background color of the text balabala in balabala will change to the specified color Border color Special note: If set to transparent, the border will not be displayed.

中文字符串: 图表方向右侧提示文字，参数格式同左侧提示文字。
Chinese string: The prompt text on the right side of the chart direction, the parameter format is the same as the prompt text on the left side.

中文字符串: 图表方向提示文字边距（距图表最两边的距离），单位：像素，自然数。
Chinese string: Margin of chart direction hint text (distance from the two sides of the chart), unit: pixel, natural number.

中文字符串: 当两趟之间测量时间相差超过多少分钟后认为在该位置有一个停机位，单位：分钟，浮点数。
Chinese string: When the measured time difference between two trips exceeds a certain number of minutes, it is considered that there is a parking space at that location. Unit: minute, floating point number.

中文字符串:
判断受停机位影响的趟的计算方式：
    ByMeter, 按米数
    ByTrip, 趟趟数
Chinese string: Calculation method for determining trips affected by parking positions: ByMeter, ByTrip, ByMeter

中文字符串: 因停机导致测量受影响的米数半径，在这个范围内的扫描趟会被标记为受停机影响，单位：米，浮点数。
Chinese string: The radius in meters that the measurement is affected by the downtime. Scans within this range will be marked as affected by the downtime. Unit: meter, floating point number.

中文字符串: 因停机导致测量受影响的趟数半径，在这个范围内的扫描趟会被标记为受停机影响，单位：趟，自然数。举例：当此值为2时，以停机位趟为中心，该趟本身及其前面紧邻的两趟和后面紧邻的两趟，合计5趟将被标记为停机位受影响趟。
Chinese string: The radius of the number of trips affected by the shutdown. The scanned trips within this range will be marked as affected by the shutdown. Unit: trip, natural number. For example: when this value is 2, with the parking stand trip as the center, the trip itself and the two trips immediately before and after it, a total of 5 trips will be marked as affected by the parking stand.

中文字符串: 是否自动修复非首架工作状态（在首架非工作且未涂布时，向处于工作状态且在多架模式下的分站发送急停命令），是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to automatically repair the non-first rack working status (when the first rack is not working and not coated, send an emergency stop command to the substations that are in working status and in multi-rack mode), yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 自动重连分站配置，配置格式为重连时间间隔，单位为秒。假设配置为“10 20 30 60”，那么代表第一次重连间隔时间为10秒，第二次重连间隔时间为20秒，依次类推，从第四次起间隔时间均为60秒。
Chinese string: Automatic reconnection substation configuration, the configuration format is the reconnection time interval, the unit is seconds. Assuming the configuration is "10 20 30 60", it means the first reconnection interval is 10 seconds, the second reconnection interval is 20 seconds, and so on. From the fourth time onwards, the interval is 60 seconds.

中文字符串: 新建卷时卷名已变更事件延迟触发秒数，单位：秒，浮点数。该参数越大越不容易造成膜卷号已变更事件重复触发。
Chinese string: The delay in triggering the volume name changed event when creating a new volume, in seconds, floating point number. The larger the parameter, the less likely it is to cause repeated triggering of the film volume name changed event.

中文字符串: 是否开启演示模式，演示模式下不输出数据文件，是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to enable the demonstration mode. In the demonstration mode, no data file is output. Yes: True, No: False.

中文字符串: 是否自动设置扫描宽度，设置的扫描宽度为 最大基材宽度+最大跟边距离*2。
Chinese string: Whether to automatically set the scanning width. The set scanning width is the maximum substrate width + maximum edge distance * 2.

中文字符串: 是否允许强制同步膜卷信息，是：True，否：False。若强制同步膜卷信息，则每次主站连接到分站上时都会推送膜卷信息到分站，若主分站卷名不一致，则分站会使用主站膜卷信息新建卷。
Chinese string: Whether to allow forced synchronization of film roll information, yes: True, no: False. If forced synchronization of film roll information is allowed, the film roll information will be pushed to the sub-station every time the master station is connected to the sub-station. If the roll names of the master and sub-stations are inconsistent, the sub-station will use the master's film roll information to create a new roll.

中文字符串: 是否允许去除数据报表左右两端的空白数据区（可减小报表文件大小），是：True，否：False。
Chinese string: Whether to allow the removal of the blank data areas on the left and right ends of the data report (to reduce the report file size), yes: True, no: False.

中文字符串: 设置后，将数据报表固定直接输出至此文件夹，必须保证路径存在，否则无法生效，字符串，例如：D:\\MyFixedData
Chinese string: After setting, the data report will be fixed and directly output to this folder. The path must exist, otherwise it will not take effect. String, for example: D:\\MyFixedData

中文字符串: 趟最大分区数量，单位：个，整数。当该值小于等于0时不限制。
Chinese string: The maximum number of partitions per pass, in units of , integer. When the value is less than or equal to 0, there is no limit.

中文字符串: 区域名称，替代报表名称中的 {region} 占位符。
Chinese string: The region name that replaces the {region} placeholder in the report name.

中文字符串:
选择要输出到文件的数据报表类型，支持以下类型报表：
    OriginalMultipleFile， 多文件原始数据报表
    OriginalSingleFile， 单文件原始数据报表
    IncrementalMultipleFile， 多文件净增数据报表
    IncrementalSingleFile， 单文件净增数据报表
Chinese string: Select the data report type to be output to the file. The following types of reports are supported: OriginalMultipleFile, multiple-file original data report OriginalSingleFile, single-file original data report IncrementalMultipleFile, multiple-file net increase data report IncrementalSingleFile, single-file net increase data report

中文字符串: 是否允许输出未匹配的数据点（净增模式下开关有效），是：True，否则：False。
Chinese string: Whether to allow the output of unmatched data points (the switch is valid in net increase mode), if yes: True, otherwise: False.

中文字符串:
参与计算净增量的架数据源定义：
    假设共有3架数据，那么1代表一架，2代表二架，3代表三架，有个特殊的标识0代表空架。
    则 3-2代表三架数据减二架得到的净增数据，1-0代表一架本身的数据（即一架数据减空架得到的净增数据）。
    支持为净增数据定义 “名称”，请使用半角“:”分隔数据定义与数据名称，例如：“2-1:B面”代表使用第二架与第一架相应的数据相减，数据名称为“B面”。若未定义数据名称，那么数据名称默认为数据定义自身，例如：“2-1”的默认数据名称为“2-1”。
    留空表示使用软件自动生成的数据源定义，例如，对于二架同步设备，就是“1-0;2-1”，对于三架设备，就是“1-0;2-1;3-2”，依此类推。
Chinese string:
The definition of the rack data source involved in calculating the net increase: 
 Assuming there are 3 racks of data, 1 represents one rack, 2 represents two racks, and 3 represents three racks. There is a special identifier 0 that represents an empty rack. 
 Then 3-2 represents the net increase data obtained by subtracting two racks from the data of three racks, and 1-0 represents the data of one rack itself (that is, the net increase data obtained by subtracting the data of one rack from the empty rack). 
 It supports defining "names" for net increase data. Please use half-width ":" to separate the data definition and the data name. For example, "2-1:B side" means subtracting the corresponding data of the second rack from the first rack, and the data name is "B side". If the data name is not defined, the data name defaults to the data definition itself. For example, the default data name of "2-1" is "2-1". 
 Leaving it blank means using the data source definition automatically generated by the software. For example, for two synchronous equipment, it is "1-0;2-1", for three equipment, it is "1-0;2-1;3-2", and so on.

中文字符串:
净增模式报表多文件模式文件名模板，支持占位符如下：

    {no} - 净增数据虚拟架号

    {subregion} - 分站区域名称

    {region} - 主站区域名称
    {product} - 产品型号
    {coating} - 涂层类型
    {timestamp} - 时间戳
    {year} - 年
    {month} - 月
    {day} - 日

The file name template of the multi-file mode of the net increase mode report supports the following placeholders:

 {submachine} - substation machine number

中文字符串:
;访问控制列表文件
;
;该文件控制软件各个角色权限所能执行的操作
;各功能点关键字及对应的功能点描述如下：
Chinese string: ;Access control list file; ;This file controls the operations that can be performed by each role of the software;The keywords of each function point and the corresponding function point are described as follows:

中文字符串:
;
;角色权限说明
;角色通过树节点的方式表达等级，本级角色可以访问本级独有的和下级所有角色可以访问的功能点。
;
;访问控制列表内部运行机制介绍：
;软件内部维护一个默认的功能点对权限需求的列表，可能随着软件升级该列表会发生变化。
;本文件的作用在于对软件内部维护的列表进行微调。
;例子1：
;前置条件：在未修改本文件之前，配方管理功能需要工程师以上权限才能访问。
;要求及应对措施：假设您要求操作员就可以访问配方管理功能，那么您可以通过将配方管理功能点关键字放在操作员行来实现这一目的。
;例子2：
;前置条件：在未修改本文件之前，选项管理功能只有工程师以上权限才能访问。
;要求及应对措施：假设您要求只有管理员才可以访问选项管理功能，那么您可以通过将选项管理功能点关键字放在管理员行来实现这一目的。
;
;访问控制列表文件格式说明：
;1、以分号为开头的行为注释行，没有实际作用，仅作为文字说明。
;2、第一行：访问控制文件格式版本号，用来记录此文件的版本号，请勿修改此值。
;3、第二行：访问控制文件功能点版本号，用来记录此文件的版本号，请勿修改此值。
;4、第三行之后：格式为“角色名称: 该角色以所有上级角色访问的功能点集合”。
;5、功能点集合中的功能点之间用空格隔开，如“Shell.A Shell.B Shell.C”。
;6、在本行之前不允许出现非注释行，否则可能导致文件解析失败。
Chinese string: ;Role permission description;Role levels are expressed in the form of tree nodes. The role at this level can access the function points that are unique to this level and accessible to all lower-level roles. ; ;Introduction to the internal operation mechanism of the access control list: ;The software maintains a default list of permission requirements for function points, which may change with software upgrades. ;The purpose of this file is to fine-tune the list maintained internally by the software. ;Example 1: ;Precondition: Before this file is modified, the recipe management function requires engineer permissions or higher to access. ;Requirements and countermeasures: If you require that operators can access the recipe management function, you can achieve this goal by placing the recipe management function point keyword in the operator line. ;Example 2: ;Precondition: Before this file is modified, the option management function can only be accessed by engineers or higher. ;Requirements and countermeasures: If you require that only administrators can access the option management function, you can achieve this goal by placing the option management function point keyword in the administrator line. ; ;Access control list file format description: ;1. Lines starting with a semicolon are comment lines, which have no actual effect and are only used as text descriptions. ;2. The first line: the access control file format version number, used to record the version number of this file. Do not modify this value. ;3. The second line: the access control file function point version number, used to record the version number of this file. Do not modify this value. ;4. After the third line: the format is "role name: the function point set that this role accesses with all superior roles". ;5. The function points in the function point set are separated by spaces, such as "Shell.A Shell.B Shell.C". ;6. Non-comment lines are not allowed before this line, otherwise the file parsing may fail.
