Chinese string: The automatic correction and rejection mode has been turned on, but the multi-channel information or substrate boundary points do not exist. All data has been filtered. Please manually find the edge first.

中文字符串: 已开启涂层外区域过滤，但涂层边数据不合理，请先手动寻边。
Chinese string: The outer area filtering of the coating has been enabled, but the coating edge data is unreasonable. Please find the edge manually first.

中文字符串: 已开启基材过滤，但基材边数据不合理，请先手动寻边。
Chinese string: Substrate filtering has been enabled, but the substrate edge data is not reasonable. Please manually find the edge first.

中文字符串: 测量数据（{beforeCount}个）已全部被按位置过滤器滤除，请检查位置过滤相关参数是否合理。
Chinese string: All measurement data ({beforeCount}) have been filtered out by the location filter. Please check whether the location filter related parameters are reasonable.

中文字符串: 设备正在测零，数据已被丢弃。
Chinese string: The device is measuring zero and the data has been discarded.

中文字符串: 最近1秒，共抖动 {_shakingCount} 次，单次最大抖动点数为 {_maxShakingPointsCount} 点。
Chinese string: In the last second, the number of shakes is {_shakingCount} times, and the maximum number of shake points for a single shake is {_maxShakingPointsCount} points.

中文字符串: 已开启削薄区过滤，但基材边数据不合理，请先手动寻边。
Chinese string: The thinning area filtering has been turned on, but the substrate edge data is unreasonable. Please find the edge manually first.

中文字符串: 已开启削薄区过滤，但未找到基材边，所有数据已过滤，请先手动寻边。
Chinese string: The chipping area filter has been turned on, but the substrate edge has not been found. All data has been filtered. Please find the edge manually first.

中文字符串: 已开启实验性实时削薄区剔除功能，但多道信息不存在，所有数据已过滤，请先手动寻边。
Chinese string: The experimental real-time thinning area removal function has been enabled, but the multi-channel information does not exist. All data has been filtered. Please manually find the edge first.

中文字符串: 已开启涂层外区域过滤，但未找到涂层边，所有数据已过滤，请先手动寻边。
Chinese string: The area filtering outside the coating has been enabled, but the coating edge has not been found. All data has been filtered. Please find the edge manually first.

中文字符串: 已开启基材边过滤，但未找到基材边，所有数据已过滤，请先手动寻边。
Chinese string: Substrate edge filtering has been enabled, but no substrate edge has been found. All data has been filtered. Please manually search for edges first.

中文字符串: 没有涂层缓存边，所有削薄区数据已剔除。
Chinese string: There is no coating cache edge, and all chipped area data has been removed.

中文字符串: 本趟数据为空，未采集到削薄区数据。
Chinese string: The data for this trip is empty, and no data on the thinning area was collected.

中文字符串: 扫描区间未覆盖涂层区域，所有削薄区数据已剔除。
Chinese string: The scanning interval does not cover the coating area, and all the thinning area data has been eliminated.
Error in processing of chipped area.

中文字符串: 该趟{dataPointResult}不完整，完整范围为{fullRange}，跳过。
Chinese string: This trip {dataPointResult} is incomplete, the full range is {fullRange}, skipped.

中文字符串: 该趟{dataPointResult}是限位趟，限位值为({_limitTripMaxY})，跳过。
Chinese string: This trip {dataPointResult} is a limit trip, the limit value is ({_limitTripMaxY}), and it is skipped.

中文字符串: 该趟{dataPointResult}含有因异常需要跳过的数据，跳过。
Chinese string: This trip {dataPointResult} contains data that needs to be skipped due to an exception, so it is skipped.

中文字符串: 最近1秒，共跳过抖动趟 {_shakingCount} 个。
Chinese string: In the last second, {_shakingCount} shaking trips were skipped.
The length of this trip is too short {dataPointResult}, skipped.
This trip contains a jump point {dataPointResult}, skip it.

中文字符串: 该趟存在异常{dataPointResult}，没有数据点，跳过。
Chinese string: This trip has an exception {dataPointResult}, no data points, skipped.

中文字符串: 本趟对应有效数据边界为：{string.Join(
Chinese string: The corresponding valid data boundary for this pass is: {string.Join(
The first Y coordinate less than 0: {0}

中文字符串: 趟分区处理后发现小于0的Y坐标，本趟数据处理失败，所有数据将被过滤，建议重新寻边！调试信息：{debugInfo}。
Chinese string: After a partitioning process, a Y coordinate less than 0 is found. This data process fails and all data will be filtered. It is recommended to search for edges again! Debug information: {debugInfo}.

中文字符串: 已启用动态调整削薄区剔除宽度功能，目前应用的削薄区剔除宽度为 {allShallowZoneWidthForCulling / 2} 毫米。
Chinese string: Dynamic adjustment of shaving zone culling width has been enabled, currently the shaving zone culling width applied is {allShallowZoneWidthForCulling / 2} mm.

中文字符串: 已开启智能分区模式，但多道信息或基材边界点不存在，所有数据已过滤，请先手动寻边。
Chinese string: The intelligent partitioning mode has been turned on, but the multi-channel information or substrate boundary points do not exist. All data has been filtered. Please manually find the edge first.

中文字符串: 膜区 {i + 1}({channelPoints.Length}) 最后一个分区数量({perPartitionCount})为 {remains}。
Chinese string: The last partition count ({perPartitionCount}) of membrane area {i + 1} ({channelPoints.Length}) is {remains}.

中文字符串: 膜区 {i + 1}({channelPoints.Length}) 最后一个分区数量({perPartitionCount})为 {remains}，数量不足，已自动补足。
Chinese string: The number of the last partitions ({perPartitionCount}) of the membrane area {i + 1} ({channelPoints.Length}) is {remains}. The number is insufficient and has been automatically supplemented.

中文字符串: 膜区 {i + 1}({channelPoints.Length}) 最后两个分区数量({perPartitionCount})分别为 {counts[inc].Count}和{counts[counts.Length - 1 - inc].Count}。
Chinese string: Membrane area {i + 1} ({channelPoints.Length}) The last two partition counts ({perPartitionCount}) are {counts[inc].Count} and {counts[counts.Length - 1 - inc].Count} respectively.

中文字符串: 膜区 {i + 1}({channelPoints.Length}) 最后两个分区数量({perPartitionCount})分别为 {counts[inc].Count}和{counts[counts.Length - 1 - inc].Count}，数量不足，已自动补足。
Chinese string: The last two partition counts ({perPartitionCount}) of membrane area {i + 1} ({channelPoints.Length}) are {counts[inc].Count} and {counts[counts.Length - 1 - inc].Count} respectively. The quantity is insufficient and has been automatically supplemented.

中文字符串: 已开启智能分区模式，但膜区或基材边界点不存在或输入的膜区个数与设备采集的不一致，所有数据已过滤，请先手动寻边。
Chinese string: The intelligent partitioning mode has been turned on, but the membrane area or substrate boundary point does not exist or the number of membrane areas entered is inconsistent with the number collected by the device. All data has been filtered. Please manually find the edge first.

中文字符串: 测量数据（{beforeCount}个）已全部被按值过滤器滤除，请检查值过滤参数是否合理。
Chinese string: All measurement data ({beforeCount}) have been filtered out by the value filter. Please check whether the value filter parameters are reasonable.

中文字符串: 因 X 方向坐标未发生变化，放弃本次输出。
Chinese string: Since the X-axis coordinates have not changed, this output is abandoned.

中文字符串: 该X方向趟长度过短{dataPointResult.ToXString()}，输出空白结果。
Chinese string: The X-direction length is too short {dataPointResult.ToXString()}, and a blank result is output.
The length of the X direction is too short {dataPointResult.ToXString()}, so it is skipped.

中文字符串: 该属性已废弃，请使用 ChannelBordersNew API。
Chinese string: This property is deprecated. Please use ChannelBordersNew API.

中文字符串: 该属性已废弃，请使用 SubstrateBordersNew API。
Chinese string: This property is deprecated, please use SubstrateBordersNew API.

中文字符串: 该属性已废弃，请使用 ChannelBeginBorderNew API。
Chinese string: This property is deprecated. Please use ChannelBeginBorderNew API.

中文字符串: 检测到设备停止扫描且标准片吸收值已修正，已清除标准片吸收修正值。
Chinese string: It is detected that the device stops scanning and the standard film absorption value has been corrected, and the standard film absorption correction value has been cleared.

中文字符串: 检测到吹扫长时间开启，已自动关闭！
Chinese string: It was detected that the purge was turned on for a long time and it was automatically turned off!

中文字符串: 寻边跟踪无法运行，请先手动寻边！
Chinese string: Edge tracking cannot be run, please manually find the edge first!

中文字符串: 本次{name}宽度({extractBorders[1] - extractBorders[0]:f2}mm)与缓存{name}宽度({cachedBorders.End - cachedBorders.Begin:f2}mm)相差大于 {AlertWidthOffset:f2}mm
Chinese string: The difference between the current {name} width ({extractBorders[1] - extractBorders[0]:f2}mm) and the cached {name} width ({cachedBorders.End - cachedBorders.Begin:f2}mm) is greater than {AlertWidthOffset:f2}mm

中文字符串: 本分析周期仅寻到单侧{name}边
Chinese string: Only one-sided {name} edge was found in this analysis cycle

中文字符串: 本分析周期预测{name}宽度({predictRightBorder - predictLeftBorder:f2}mm)与缓存{name}宽度({cachedBorders.End - cachedBorders.Begin:f2}mm)相差大于 {AlertWidthOffset:f2}mm
Chinese string: The difference between the predicted {name} width ({predictRightBorder - predictLeftBorder:f2}mm) and the cached {name} width ({cachedBorders.End - cachedBorders.Begin:f2}mm) during this analysis period is greater than {AlertWidthOffset:f2}mm

中文字符串: {dataChannel} 因{reason}，且未开启自动扩边功能，无法完成扩边操作！
Chinese string: {dataChannel} cannot complete the edge expansion operation due to {reason} and the automatic edge expansion function is not enabled!

中文字符串: {dataChannel} 因{reason}，且处于模拟状态或多架模式无法完成自动扩边操作，请及时处理！
Chinese string: {dataChannel} cannot complete the automatic edge expansion operation due to {reason} and is in simulation state or multi-rack mode. Please handle it in time!

中文字符串: {dataChannel} 因{reason}，且本次扩边宽度为 {expandWidth:f2}mm，已超过最大允许扩边宽度({AutoExpandLimitWidth}mm)，无法完成扩边操作，请及时处理！
Chinese string: {dataChannel} Due to {reason}, and the current expansion width is {expandWidth:f2}mm, it has exceeded the maximum allowable expansion width ({AutoExpandLimitWidth}mm), and the expansion operation cannot be completed. Please handle it in time!

中文字符串: {dataChannel} 因{reason}，且本次扩边目标起止点为 ({left:f2}mm, {right:f2}mm)，均已超越有效扫描区间({ValidBegin}mm, {ValidEnd}mm)，无法完成扩边操作，请及时处理！
Chinese string: {dataChannel} Due to {reason}, the starting and ending points of this edge expansion target are ({left:f2}mm, {right:f2}mm), both of which have exceeded the valid scanning range ({ValidBegin}mm, {ValidEnd}mm), and the edge expansion operation cannot be completed. Please handle it in time!

中文字符串: {dataChannel} 因{reason}，开始尝试扩边，扩边起止点为 ({left:f2}mm, {right:f2}mm)。
Chinese string: {dataChannel} starts to try to expand the edge due to {reason}, and the starting and ending points of the expansion are ({left:f2}mm, {right:f2}mm).

中文字符串: {dataChannel} 偏移方向不同，预计实际偏移较小，不予修正。
Chinese string: {dataChannel} is offset in a different direction, the actual offset is expected to be smaller, and no correction will be made.

中文字符串: {dataChannel} 寻边跟踪成功，边界偏移量为：
Chinese string: {dataChannel} Edge tracking is successful, the boundary offset is:

中文字符串: {dataChannel} 本次检测到的实际扫描区间偏移量({realOffset:f2}mm)小于可忽略偏移量({IgnoreOffset}mm)，偏移量较小，不予修正。
Chinese string: {dataChannel} The actual scanning interval offset ({realOffset:f2}mm) detected this time is less than the negligible offset ({IgnoreOffset}mm). The offset is small and will not be corrected.

中文字符串: {dataChannel} 因 本次检测到的实际扫描区间偏移量({realOffset:f2}mm)大于等于可忽略偏移量({IgnoreOffset}mm)，将平移扫描区间。
Chinese string: {dataChannel} Since the actual scanning interval offset ({realOffset:f2}mm) detected this time is greater than or equal to the negligible offset ({IgnoreOffset}mm), the scanning interval will be shifted.

中文字符串: {dataChannel} 执行动作3，重置上次扩边宽度为空
Chinese string: {dataChannel} executes action 3 and resets the last expansion width to empty

中文字符串: {dataChannel} 执行动作5，清除左右边界缓存。
Chinese string: {dataChannel} executes action 5 and clears the left and right boundary caches.

中文字符串: {dataChannel} 执行动作6，按需消除寻边跟踪异常。
Chinese string: {dataChannel} executes action 6 to eliminate edge tracking anomalies as needed.

中文字符串: 发生事件4，用户手动寻边或连接重置。
Chinese string: Event 4 occurs: the user manually searches for an edge or the connection is reset.

中文字符串: {dataChannel} 寻边跟踪已由 {oldState.GetDisplayName()} 状态进入 {newState.GetDisplayName()} 状态。
Chinese string: {dataChannel} edge tracking has entered the {newState.GetDisplayName()} state from the {oldState.GetDisplayName()} state.

中文字符串: 激光寻边跟踪无法运行
Chinese string: Laser edge tracking does not work

中文字符串: 激光寻边跟踪无法运行，请先手动寻边！
Chinese string: Laser edge tracking cannot run, please manually find the edge first!

中文字符串: 本次基材宽度({extractBorders[1] - extractBorders[0]:f2}mm)与历史基材宽度({cachedBorders.End - cachedBorders.Begin:f2}mm)相差大于 {AlertWidthOffset:f2}mm
Chinese string: The difference between the current substrate width ({extractBorders[1] - extractBorders[0]:f2}mm) and the historical substrate width ({cachedBorders.End - cachedBorders.Begin:f2}mm) is greater than {AlertWidthOffset:f2}mm
Only one side of the substrate is found
{dataChannel} {event2ErrorInfo}, The slave channel does not support edge expansion.

中文字符串: 本分析周期仅寻到单侧基材边
Chinese string: This analysis cycle only found one side of the substrate edge

中文字符串: 本分析周期预测基材宽度({predictRightBorder - predictLeftBorder:f2}mm)与历史基材宽度({cachedBorders.End - cachedBorders.Begin:f2}mm)相差大于 {AlertWidthOffset:f2}mm
Chinese string: The predicted substrate width ({predictRightBorder - predictLeftBorder:f2}mm) of this analysis period differs from the historical substrate width ({cachedBorders.End - cachedBorders.Begin:f2}mm) by more than {AlertWidthOffset:f2}mm
{dataChannel} {event2ErrorInfo}, The slave channel does not support edge expansion.

中文字符串: 正在涂布且不允许涂布时提取边界，设置缓存边失败！
Chinese string: Extracting borders while coating is in progress and coating is not allowed, setting cache edges failed!
The result of this edge search ({string.Join(

中文字符串: , Enumerable.Repeat(parameters.SubstrateWidth, 1).Concat(parameters.ChannelWidths))})相差较大(超过{AlertWidthOffset})，已自动降级为寻边跟踪。
Chinese string: , Enumerable.Repeat(parameters.SubstrateWidth, 1).Concat(parameters.ChannelWidths))}) is quite different (exceeding {AlertWidthOffset}), and has been automatically downgraded to edge tracking.

中文字符串: 本次寻边基材宽度({rightY - leftY})与历史基材边宽度({oldSubstrateBorders.Value.End - oldSubstrateBorders.Value.Begin})相差较大(超过{AlertWidthOffset})，无法更新边界点偏移量。
Chinese string: The width of the substrate for edge search ({rightY - leftY}) is significantly different from the width of the historical substrate border ({oldSubstrateBorders.Value.End - oldSubstrateBorders.Value.Begin}) (exceeding {AlertWidthOffset}), so the boundary point offset cannot be updated.

中文字符串: 历史基材边不存，无法更新边界点偏移量。
Chinese string: The historical substrate edge does not exist and the boundary point offset cannot be updated.
The result of this edge search ({string.Join(

中文字符串: , Enumerable.Repeat(parameters.SubstrateWidth, 1).Concat(parameters.ChannelWidths))})相差较大(超过{AlertWidthOffset})，设置缓存边失败！
Chinese string: , Enumerable.Repeat(parameters.SubstrateWidth, 1).Concat(parameters.ChannelWidths))}) is quite different (exceeding {AlertWidthOffset}), setting cache edge failed!

中文字符串: 未能提取到基材边界，设置缓存边失败！
Chinese string: Failed to extract the substrate boundary, failed to set cache edge!

中文字符串: 寻峰设置分析成功，基材边峰值：{result.Value.SubstratePeakLow}，涂层峰值：{result.Value.CoatingPeakLow}。
Chinese string: The peak search setting analysis was successful, substrate edge peak value: {result.Value.SubstratePeakLow}, coating peak value: {result.Value.CoatingPeakLow}.

中文字符串: 未能分析到基材、极片边，放弃调整。
Chinese string: Failed to analyze the substrate and the edge of the electrode, so gave up the adjustment.

中文字符串: 已开启自动调整寻边参数功能，但没有任何数据，放弃调整。
Chinese string: The automatic adjustment of edge-finding parameters has been enabled, but there is no data, so the adjustment is abandoned.

中文字符串: 已开启自动调整寻边参数功能，但不支持当前的边界检测模式（{options.BorderDetectMode}），放弃调整。
Chinese string: The automatic adjustment of edge detection parameters has been enabled, but the current border detection mode ({options.BorderDetectMode}) is not supported, so the adjustment is abandoned.

中文字符串: 已添加的点与总点数不等，可能有些点没有输出到文件中。
Chinese string: The added points are not equal to the total number of points, and some points may not be output to the file.

中文字符串: 遇到问题，数据未能保存到数据库。
Chinese string: A problem occurred and the data could not be saved to the database.

中文字符串: 很抱歉，因某些故障，数据未能保存到数据库，并且已自动关闭 保存到数据库 功能！
Chinese string: Sorry, due to some failure, the data could not be saved to the database, and the save to database function has been automatically closed!

中文字符串: {FilterEnvironment.DataChannel} 当前系统算力已严重不足，过滤器 {filterNode.Filter} 已积压 {queue.Count} 批数据，将自动丢弃一些积压的数据。
Chinese string: {FilterEnvironment.DataChannel} The current system computing power is seriously insufficient. The filter {filterNode.Filter} has a backlog of {queue.Count} batches of data. Some of the backlog data will be automatically discarded.

中文字符串: 只有在数据线程上执行的过滤器才能在后续处理中开启新线程。
Chinese string: Only filters executed on the data thread can start new threads for subsequent processing.

中文字符串: {FilterEnvironment.DataChannel} 过滤器 {filterNode.Filter} 新线程数据处理时间：{Environment.TickCount - tick} 毫秒。
Chinese string: {FilterEnvironment.DataChannel} filter {filterNode.Filter} new thread data processing time: {Environment.TickCount - tick} milliseconds.

中文字符串: {FilterEnvironment.DataChannel} 过滤器 {filterNode.Filter} 新线程数据处理失败。
Chinese string: {FilterEnvironment.DataChannel} filter {filterNode.Filter} new thread data processing failed.

中文字符串: 当前过滤器配置管理器已在应用中，不能再次应用！
Chinese string: The current filter configuration manager is already applied and cannot be applied again!

中文字符串: 自动启停：要求设备温补初始化后启动扫描。
Chinese string: Automatic start and stop: requires the device to start scanning after temperature compensation is initialized.

中文字符串: 自动启停：要求设备测量零点后启动扫描。
Chinese string: Automatic start and stop: Requires the device to start scanning after measuring the zero point.

中文字符串: 自动启停：要求设备启动扫描。
Chinese string: Auto Start and Stop: Requires the device to initiate scanning.

中文字符串: 自动启停：要求设备停止扫描。
Chinese string: Automatic start and stop: Request the device to stop scanning.
User turns off automatic start and stop
User turns off automatic start and stop

中文字符串: 当前处于单架模式，无法启动多架扫描，请先切换到多架模式！
Chinese string: Currently in single-frame mode, multi-frame scanning cannot be started. Please switch to multi-frame mode first!

中文字符串: 自动启停：要求设备测量零点。
Chinese string: Automatic start and stop: Requires the device to measure zero point.

中文字符串: 检测到基材宽度或膜区宽度发生变化，下次启动扫描将自动寻边。
Chinese string: If a change in the substrate width or film area width is detected, the next scan will automatically find the edge.

中文字符串: 自动启停已开启，无法完成 {actionName} 操作！
Chinese string: Automatic start/stop is enabled, unable to complete {actionName} operation!

中文字符串: 检测到分站部分关键线程卡死，卡死的线程为{errorMessage}，请及时处理！
Chinese string: It was detected that some key threads of the substation were stuck. The stuck thread is {errorMessage}. Please handle it in time!

中文字符串: 检测到所有关键线程已恢复正常运行，分站冻结异常已消除！
Chinese string: It has been detected that all key threads have resumed normal operation and the substation freezing anomaly has been eliminated!

中文字符串: 检测到 自动启停 启动扫描失败，请及时处理！
Chinese string: It is detected that the automatic start-stop startup scan failed, please handle it in time!

中文字符串: 检测到 不再需要启动扫描或设备已启动扫描，警报消除。
Chinese string: The alarm is cleared when it detects that a scan is no longer needed or the device has already started scanning.

中文字符串: 发生器位置为 {y1} 毫米，探测器位置为 {y2} 毫米，相对距离为 {relativeDistance} 毫米。
Chinese string: The generator position is {y1} mm, the detector position is {y2} mm, and the relative distance is {relativeDistance} mm.

中文字符串: 发生器与探测器的相对位置已恢复，同步超差异常已消除。
Chinese string: The relative position of the generator and the detector has been restored and the synchronization excess error has been eliminated.

中文字符串: 检测到 管电压[{EnvironmentVariables.TubeVoltageForDisplay} V]或管电流[{EnvironmentVariables.TubeCurrentForDisplay} uA] 未达到设定值，请及时处理！
Chinese string: It is detected that the tube voltage [{EnvironmentVariables.TubeVoltageForDisplay} V] or tube current [{EnvironmentVariables.TubeCurrentForDisplay} uA] has not reached the set value, please handle it in time!

中文字符串: 检测到 管电压与管电流已达到正常范围，警报已消除。
Chinese string: It was detected that the tube voltage and tube current have reached the normal range and the alarm has been eliminated.

中文字符串: 因设备停止扫描，超限警报已自动消除！
